{"type":"compaction","id":"3b8a1123","parentId":"1c504bb9","timestamp":"2026-04-23T16:14:40.993Z","summary":"## Goal\n- Fix issues in the AHV QLHV projects (`ahv-qlhv-fe`, `ahv-qlhv-be`) and MAIY Tech Hub ecosystem according to user requests, with branch-per-task and commit-only workflow.\n- Also maintain uptime of services: report portal (8790), MAIY Tech Hub frontend (3000), MAIY Tech Hub backend (4000).\n- New goal (current): Make start/end time and duration independent in both DAT forms, with validation that duration ≤ (end time − start time).\n\n## Constraints & Preferences\n- Always use prompt-optimizer first to clarify, then confirm with user, then implement.\n- Do not type code directly unless via workflow/agent when possible.\n- Must **checkout a new branch before doing work**.\n- Must **not push**. Only **commit** after finishing.\n- Local only agent ecosystem, no GitLab push.\n- MongoDB only, no PostgreSQL.\n- User language preference: Vietnamese.\n\n## Progress\n### Done\n- [x] **Fixed DAT action disabled on Progress page without enrollment** (from previous context)\n  - Branch: `fix/progress-dat-disable-without-enrollment-20260423`\n  - Commit: `aedf1f6` — `fix: disable DAT action on progress page without enrollment`\n  - File: `src/app/progress/page.tsx`\n  - Behavior: button disabled + \"Chưa vào khóa\" label when no enrollment\n- [x] **Confirmed health check persistence fix in backend**\n  - Branch: `fix/health-profile-update-persist-20260423`\n  - Commit: `46afadc` — `fix: persist health check update without existing enrollment`\n- [x] **Fixed add-student course/rank sync**\n  - Branch: `fix/student-add-course-rank-sync-20260423`\n  - Commit: `963244c` — `fix: sync student course selection with license rank`\n- [x] **Fixed \"Đợt thu phí\" settings tab was hidden**\n  - Branch: `fix/restore-fee-batch-settings-tab-20260423`\n  - Commit: `39f0595` — `fix: restore fee batch settings tab`\n  - Root cause: `GeneralSettingsView` switch missing `case 'dot-thu': return <FeeBatchManagement ... />;` in `src/app/settings/page.tsx`\n- [x] **Synced Student Detail DAT form with Progress page DAT form**\n  - Branch: `fix/sync-student-detail-dat-form-with-progress-20260423`\n  - Commit: `b499906` — `fix: sync student detail DAT form with progress page`\n  - File: `src/components/students/modules/DatSessionModal.tsx`\n  - Added: `FieldWrapper` component, time auto-sync logic, validation, reset on open, matching UI with progress page\n- [x] **Fixed frontend API base URL for external VPS access**\n  - Branch: `fix/external-login-api-base-url-20260423`\n  - Commit: `5c6dfe3` — `fix: resolve external login API base URL`\n  - File: `src/services/api.ts`\n  - Changed: `getBaseUrl()` now uses `window.location.protocol + '//' + window.location.hostname + ':5002'` for non-localhost hosts\n- [x] **Fixed backend CORS whitelist for external frontend**\n  - Branch: `fix/allow-external-fe-cors-20260423`\n  - Commit: `48d97e5` — `fix: allow external frontend origin for CORS`\n  - File: `src/app.ts`\n  - Added to `ALLOWED_ORIGINS`: `'http://localhost:3002'`, `'http://103.253.21.139:3002'`\n- [x] **Fixed .env duplicate MongoDB config blocks causing auth failures**\n  - Cleaned: removed old block with `MONGODB_URI=mongodb://103.253.21.98:27017`, `MONGODB_USER`, `MONGODB_PASS`; removed stale `JWT_EXPIRES_IN=7d` duplicate block; kept only one clean block with `MONGODB_URI=mongodb://localhost:27017`, `MONGODB_NAME=ahv_qlhv`, `JWT_SECRET`, `JWT_REFRESH_SECRET`\n  - Later user supplied updated `.env` with production values: `MONGODB_URI=mongodb://103.253.21.98:27017`, `MONGODB_NAME=dtlx`, `MONGODB_USER=root`, `MONGODB_PASS=RYLoQJqsDr4EQIJB`, `JWT_SECRET=super_secret_jwt_key_at_least_32_chars_1234`\n- [x] **Restarted backend 5002** with correct `.env` after fixing duplicate config; verified login now returns `{\"success\":false,\"message\":\"Invalid credentials\"}` (proper error, not system error)\n- [x] **Restarted report portal at port 8790** — `python3 -m http.server 8790 -d /root/.openclaw/workspaces2/v4-ecosystem-review/master-orchestrator/docs/report-portal` — confirmed `HTTP 200 OK`\n- [x] **Created uptime monitor for 8790, 3000 (MAIY FE), 4000 (MAIY BE)**\n  - Scripts created in `/root/.openclaw/workspaces2/v4-ecosystem-review/master-orchestrator/scripts/`:\n    - `start-report-portal-8790.sh`\n    - `start-maiy-frontend-3000.sh`\n    - `start-maiy-backend-4000.sh`\n    - `monitor-services.sh`\n  - Cron installed: `* * * * * /root/.openclaw/workspaces2/v4-ecosystem-review/master-orchestrator/scripts/monitor-services.sh >/tmp/monitor-services-cron.log 2>&1`\n  - Status: 8790 and MAIY FE 3000 running; MAIY BE 4000 crashes on startup due to MongoDB plugin timeout\n\n### In Progress\n- [ ] **Making DAT duration field independent from start/end time** — awaiting user confirmation\n  - User's clarification: start time, end time, and duration are 3 independent fields; no auto-sync between them; but validate on submit: `duration ≤ (end_time − start_time)`\n  - Applies to both: `src/components/students/modules/DatSessionModal.tsx` (Student Detail) and `src/components/progress/AddDatModal.tsx` (Progress page)\n\n### Blocked\n- MAIY Tech Hub backend (4000) crashes on startup: `FastifyError: Plugin did not start in time: 'mongodb'`. Monitor will restart but will keep failing until root cause is fixed.\n- FE production build blocked by existing repo issue: `Cannot find module '@playwright/test'` in `playwright.config.ts`.\n\n## Key Decisions\n- **Health check data belongs to enrollment**: Root cause was backend enrollment-linked persistence logic.\n- **Student Detail DAT blocked at UI when no enrollment**: Prevent invalid add flow instead of relying on backend failure.\n- **Add Student form auto-maps rank from selected course**: User requested \"Khi chưa chọn thì show tất cả khóa khi chọn một khóa tự động mapping hạng bằng\".\n- **API base URL uses same hostname as FE**: Non-localhost FE should call API on same hostname, not fallback to `127.0.0.1`.\n- **CORS whitelist includes both localhost variants and VPS IP**: Backend must explicitly allow the external frontend origin.\n- **.env duplicate blocks cause env-var collision**: Node.js reads entire `.env` file; old `MONGODB_USER`/`MONGODB_PASS` from top block persist even if bottom block omits them.\n- **Cron-based process monitor instead of systemd**: Simple shell scripts + crontab to restart services every minute.\n- **Duration and time fields are independent with submission-time validation**: User explicitly wants no auto-sync between duration and time fields.\n\n## Next Steps\n1. Wait for user confirmation on the DAT duration/time independence change, then implement in both forms.\n2. Fix MAIY Tech Hub backend MongoDB plugin startup timeout (port 4000).\n3. After fixing DAT forms, commit on new branch and optionally restart services for testing.\n\n## Critical Context\n- Khuong / Khương Nịnh, prefers Vietnamese.\n- FE: `/root/.openclaw/workspaces2/projects/ahv-qlhv-fe`\n- BE: `/root/.openclaw/workspaces2/projects/ahv-qlhv-be`\n- MAIY FE: `/root/.openclaw/workspaces2/v4-ecosystem-review/maiy-tech-hub` (port 3000)\n- MAIY BE: `/root/.openclaw/workspaces2/projects/maiy-tech-hub-be` (port 4000)\n- Report portal: `/root/.openclaw/workspaces2/v4-ecosystem-review/master-orchestrator/docs/report-portal` (port 8790)\n- Current BE `.env` uses: `MONGODB_URI=mongodb://103.253.21.98:27017`, `MONGODB_NAME=dtlx`, `JWT_SECRET=super_secret_jwt_key_at_least_32_chars_1234`, `JWT_REFRESH_SECRET=super_secret_refresh_key_at_least_32_chars_5678`\n- DAT forms to modify:\n  - Student Detail: `src/components/students/modules/DatSessionModal.tsx`\n  - Progress page: `src/components/progress/AddDatModal.tsx`\n- DatSessionModal uses `enrollmentId` prop; AddDatModal uses `enrollmentId?: string` prop\n- Services monitor scripts at: `/root/.openclaw/workspaces2/v4-ecosystem-review/master-orchestrator/scripts/`\n- Cron for monitor: `* * * * * /root/.openclaw/workspaces2/v4-ecosystem-review/master-orchestrator/scripts/monitor-services.sh`\n\n---\n\n**Turn Context (split turn):**\n\n## Original Request\nUser confirmed something (likely approval of a previous plan) with \"đúng rồi\" (correct/that's right).\n\n## Early Progress\n- Assistant created a new branch: `fix/dat-duration-independent-validation-20260423`\n- Assistant read both DAT form files to understand current implementation:\n  - `AddDatModal.tsx` - has `FieldWrapper` component, `DatFormData` interface, `initialState`, with fields: date, timeStart, timeEnd, duration, distance, note\n  - `DatSessionModal.tsx` - similar structure with `syncDuration` and `syncEndTime` helper functions for syncing time and duration fields\n\n## Context for Suffix\nThe goal is to refactor both DAT forms to have **3 independent fields** (date, timeStart, timeEnd, duration) and only validate that `duration <= time difference between start and end`. The suffix likely contains the actual code changes and validation logic implementation.\n\n<read-files>\n/root/.openclaw/workspaces2/projects/ahv-qlhv-be/src/application/services/dat.service.ts\n/root/.openclaw/workspaces2/projects/ahv-qlhv-be/src/infrastructure/database/models/course_student.model.ts\n/root/.openclaw/workspaces2/projects/ahv-qlhv-be/src/infrastructure/database/models/dat_session.model.ts\n/root/.openclaw/workspaces2/projects/ahv-qlhv-be/src/infrastructure/database/models/student.model.ts\n/root/.openclaw/workspaces2/projects/ahv-qlhv-be/src/infrastructure/database/mongodb.ts\n/root/.openclaw/workspaces2/projects/ahv-qlhv-be/src/infrastructure/repositories/student.repository.ts\n/root/.openclaw/workspaces2/projects/ahv-qlhv-be/src/interface/controllers/auth.controller.ts\n/root/.openclaw/workspaces2/projects/ahv-qlhv-be/src/interface/controllers/dat.controller.ts\n/root/.openclaw/workspaces2/projects/ahv-qlhv-be/src/interface/controllers/student.controller.ts\n/root/.openclaw/workspaces2/projects/ahv-qlhv-be/src/interface/