{"type":"message","id":"0faf0c50","parentId":"e405798f","timestamp":"2026-04-23T16:14:52.527Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I understand the issue. Let me look at the `validateProfile` function and the `requiredFields` from settings. The issue is:\n\n1. The `requiredFields` array in system settings likely includes `tuition` or a related field\n2. The `validateProfile` function requires all fields in `requiredFields`\n3. But `tuition` (Tổng học phí) should be optional - it should either be auto-filled from the course or just optional\n\nLet me look at what the settings `requiredFields` might contain, and where the \"vui lòng nhập tuition\" error could come from.\n\n\nI need to trace through the validation logic to see if `tuition` is actually in the `requiredFields` array and causing the validation to fail, or if there's another source of that error message.","thinkingSignature":"5fa9daf2e87dea12c31cc8899286d187c23fe649fcceeae53f04ff477ae055c0"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_hxouvyqh5aeh_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"grep -n \"tuition\\|Tổng học phí\\|vui lòng.*học phí\\|vui lòng.*đăng ký\" src/components/students/StudentDetailDrawer.tsx | head -30","workdir":"/root/.openclaw/workspaces2/projects/ahv-qlhv-fe","yieldMs":10000,"timeout":30}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_hxouvyqh5aeh_2","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"grep -n \"requiredFields\" src/components/students/StudentDetailDrawer.tsx","workdir":"/root/.openclaw/workspaces2/projects/ahv-qlhv-fe","yieldMs":10000,"timeout":30}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":1129,"output":387,"cacheRead":11152,"cacheWrite":22796,"totalTokens":35464,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776960883586,"responseId":"06397875ae4b7eb2229c535040487fe3"}}
