{"type":"message","id":"259c7aa3","parentId":"b410a39e","timestamp":"2026-04-23T16:15:33.960Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_6tcf8md95a29_2","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"                      touched={profileTouched.rank}\n                    >\n                      <select\n                        name=\"rank\"\n                        required={isFieldRequired('rank')}\n                        value={selectedRank}\n                        onBlur={() => setProfileTouched((prev) => ({ ...prev, rank: true }))}\n                        onChange={(e) => {\n                          const val = e.target.value;\n                          setSelectedRank(val);\n\n                          // Auto-fill logic for rank change\n                          if (!isFeeManuallySet) {\n                            const selectedCat = licenseCats.find((lc: any) => lc._id === val);\n                            if (selectedCat && selectedCat.fee) {\n                              setCurrentFee(formatNumberWithDots(selectedCat.fee.replace(/[^0-9]/g, '')));\n                            }\n                          }\n\n                          if (profileTouched.rank) {\n                            setProfileErrors((prev) => ({\n                              ...prev,\n                              rank: val ? '' : 'Vui lòng chọn Hạng bằng.',\n                            }));\n                          }\n                        }}\n                        className={`w-full px-3 py-2.5 bg-white border rounded-xl focus:outline-none focus:ring-4 transition-all ${\n                          profileTouched.rank && profileErrors.rank\n                            ? 'border-rose-300 focus:ring-rose-500/10 focus:border-rose-500 bg-rose-50/20'\n                            : 'border-gray-200 focus:ring-indigo-500/10 focus:border-indigo-500'\n                        } text-sm font-bold text-gray-700`}\n                      >\n                        <option value=\"\">-- Chọn Hạng bằng --</option>\n                        {licenseCats?.map((lc: any) => (\n                          <option key={lc._id} value={lc._id}>\n                            {lc.name}\n                          </option>\n                        ))}\n                      </select>\n                    </FieldWrapper>\n\n[1439 more lines in file. Use offset=1040 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1776960933953}}
{"type":"message","id":"c04e9de9","parentId":"259c7aa3","timestamp":"2026-04-23T16:15:40.740Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The logic looks good:\n1. `validateProfile` now skips `fee` (always optional) ✅\n2. When `fullData` loads, `currentFee` is initialized from `fullData.enrollment?.fee` or `fullData.course_id?.course_fee` ✅\n3. When user selects a course in the dropdown, `onCourseSelect` auto-fills from `course.course_fee` (if not manually set) ✅\n4. When user changes rank, `onChange` auto-fills from `selectedCat.fee` (if not manually set) ✅\n\n\n5. `setIsFeeManuallySet(false)` resets the manual override whenever `fullData` changes, ensuring the auto-fill logic stays active ✅\n\nSo the fix is working as intended.\n\nNow I need to commit these changes.","thinkingSignature":"7df08e9af23a21cd51d78b82cabc548878a06eccea746090bd9a1b59453a4efe"},{"type":"text","text":"Logic đã đúng rồi. Việc fix `validateProfile` loại bỏ `fee` khỏi bắt buộc là đủ. Mình commit.\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_npsn9lf5ugmp_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"git diff src/components/students/StudentDetailDrawer.tsx | head -30","workdir":"/root/.openclaw/workspaces2/projects/ahv-qlhv-fe","yieldMs":10000,"timeout":30}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":822,"output":299,"cacheRead":39170,"cacheWrite":772,"totalTokens":41063,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776960933966,"responseId":"063978a7be8fa7750e1680a7f97856e2"}}
