{"type":"message","id":"1da39028","parentId":"208264ed","timestamp":"2026-04-23T16:19:40.020Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Found it! The error message \"Vui lòng nhập học phí.\" is in `AddStudentModal.tsx` line 183:\n\n```js\nif (requiredFields.includes('tuition') && (!data.tuition || data.tuition === '0')) errs.tuition = 'Vui lòng nhập học phí.';\n```\n\nBut the Student Detail Drawer is separate from AddStudentModal. The StudentDetailDrawer doesn't have this error message. So where is \"Vui lòng nhập tuition\" coming from?\n\nWait - the user said \"vui lòng nhập tuition\". \n\nLet me search more carefully. I'm looking at the StudentDetailDrawer code and I see `validateProfile` is being called, but I fixed that function to exclude `fee` from validation. The error must be coming from somewhere else - let me trace through the submit handler to see what's actually triggering the validation.\n\nLooking at line 825 where `requiredFields` is being iterated and set as touched, but that doesn't include tuition. The `validateProfile` function shouldn't be throwing a \"Vui lòng nhập tuition\" error either since I modified it to not validate `fee`. So either there's another validation path I'm missing, or the user is triggering validation from a different component or action than the form submission I'm looking at. The message format \"Vui lòng nhập tuition\" with \"tuition\" in English is different from the Vietnamese error I found in AddStudentModal, so let me search for where this exact English string is being used in the codebase. Ah, I see the issue now—the user mentioned \"Vui lòng nhập tuition\" but the actual error message in the code is \"Vui lòng nhập học phí\", so these are the same problem. The real bug is in `AddStudentModal.tsx` line 183 where it validates that `tuition` is included in `requiredFields` before allowing submission. Since this component is used when adding a new student, the fix is to make the tuition field optional there as well, matching what I did for the fee field in StudentDetailDrawer.","thinkingSignature":"e7492659ba8cb02431a04c3e29c305d55b74d49dfb135b51cf95bd0c8fcb0f96"},{"type":"text","text":"Tìm ra rồi! Thông báo đến từ `AddStudentModal.tsx` — form thêm học viên. Mình sửa luôn ở đó.\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_oog26zvwuy4e_1","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/root/.openclaw/workspaces2/projects/ahv-qlhv-fe/src/components/students/AddStudentModal.tsx","offset":175,"limit":20}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":1114,"output":578,"cacheRead":40385,"cacheWrite":675,"totalTokens":42752,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776961166250,"responseId":"0639798ff02c5005052d0aede39fcfcf"}}
