{"type":"message","id":"efa49fc9","parentId":"1f8394eb","timestamp":"2026-04-23T16:48:56.049Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user wants:\n1. When a course ends, the status changes to \"Kết thúc\"\n2. The notification appears on the dashboard when the teacher logs in\n3. The user is concerned about popup fatigue - there are already 2 popups (new features update, welcome popup), and now we need to add another notification. They want to avoid overwhelming the teacher with multiple popups.\n\nSo I need to think about how to integrate this notification smoothly without adding another popup. Some options:\n1. Show a non-intrusive banner/card on the dashboard that can be dismissed\n2. Show a small notification badge/bell indicator\n3. Show a single combined notification that includes both \"new features\" + \"courses starting/ending today\" - but this might be complex\n\n\n4. Add it as a dashboard widget/card that stays visible until the teacher dismisses or interacts with it, rather than a modal that blocks the screen\n\nSince the user specifically said the notification should appear on the dashboard, I think the cleanest approach is to add a non-blocking alert banner or card at the top of the dashboard - something that catches attention but doesn't interrupt the teacher's workflow like a modal would. I'm realizing there might already be a dashboard welcome banner in place, so I should check what the current setup looks like before deciding on the exact placement for this notification.","thinkingSignature":"b7bfdc92607f7e203053b957a4b880e35e9da80d61d8e7c55ba0b6a3340f3bbf"},{"type":"text","text":"Mình hiểu rồi — tránh popup, gộp chung vào dashboard. Mình confirm lại:\n\n---\n\n**Giải pháp:** Thay vì popup mới, mình sẽ hiện **một banner/thông báo ngay trên dashboard** (dạng card) — không che màn hình, không block, thầy có thể bỏ qua hoặc tương tác.\n\n**Nội dung banner:**\n- Nếu có khoá khai giảng hôm nay → hiện: *\"Có N khoá khai giảng hôm nay\"* + 2 nút [Tự động] [Cập nhật tay]\n- Nếu có khoá kết thúc hôm nay → hiện: *\"Có N khoá kết thúc hôm nay\"* + 2 nút [Tự động] [Cập nhật tay]\n- Có thể gộp cả 2 vào 1 banner nếu cùng ngày\n\n**Popup cũ vẫn giữ nguyên** — không thêm popup mới.\n\n---\n\n**Đúng ý này?** Mình sẽ check dashboard hiện tại để xem đặt banner ở đâu cho hợp lý, rồi bắt đầu làm."}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":76,"output":611,"cacheRead":85411,"cacheWrite":1417,"totalTokens":87515,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776962923339,"responseId":"0639806ce16baf64d694d195d48149c2"}}
