{"type":"message","id":"45d78ddf","parentId":"13c7cb92","timestamp":"2026-04-23T16:50:38.522Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"OK so:\n- `CourseModel` has `status: 'draft' | 'ongoing' | 'completed' | 'canceled'` — this is the course template status\n- `CourseStudentModel` has `status_detail: string` — this is per-enrollment status like \"Chờ KSK\", \"Đang học\", etc.\n\nBut the user mentions \"Sắp khai giảng\" status. Let me check what the possible values of `status_detail` in CourseStudent are.\n\nActually, looking at the user's request: \"tự động chuyển trạng thái từ sắp KG -> Đang học\". \n\nSo this is definitely about the enrollment status, not the course template itself. I need to check the course routes and controller to see how these statuses are actually managed and what endpoints are available for updating them.","thinkingSignature":"3d5cd5092f91cbb17eecf65073bcc3144413c993a89e6515bb43ba4d21aea50c"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_51wlt1ew0p5j_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"grep -n \"status_detail\\|Sắp KG\\|Sắp khai giảng\\|updateCourseStudent\\|course_student\" src/interface/controllers/course.controller.ts | head -20","workdir":"/root/.openclaw/workspaces2/projects/ahv-qlhv-be","yieldMs":5000,"timeout":10}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_51wlt1ew0p5j_2","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cat src/interface/routes/course.routes.ts","workdir":"/root/.openclaw/workspaces2/projects/ahv-qlhv-be","yieldMs":5000,"timeout":10}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":185,"output":376,"cacheRead":90229,"cacheWrite":597,"totalTokens":91387,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776963030325,"responseId":"063980d7445f011ec5f450dd0956799e"}}
