{"type":"message","id":"18cba288","parentId":"780f8e56","timestamp":"2026-04-23T16:51:04.963Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"So `Course.status = 'draft'` maps to \"Sắp khai giảng\". And the transition would be `'draft'` → `'ongoing'` (`\"Đang học\"`).\n\nAnd `Course.status = 'completed'` would be \"Kết thúc\".\n\nSo the feature is about:\n1. Finding courses where:\n   - `Course.start_date === today` AND `Course.status === 'draft'` (Sắp KG) AND teacher is assigned to that course (via CourseStudent.teacher_id)\n   - `Course.end_date === today` AND `Course.status === 'ongoing'` (Đang học) AND teacher is assigned\n\n\n2. For the auto-update, I need to transition the course status from 'draft' to 'ongoing' when it starts, and from 'ongoing' to 'completed' when it ends. Now I'm looking at the course constants to understand the full status mapping.","thinkingSignature":"b9ef8138f098e56767501261e027ad87fefb02db7c3c479daef2493358003f68"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_tkuq2ug4ykzq_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cat src/domain/constants/course.constants.ts","workdir":"/root/.openclaw/workspaces2/projects/ahv-qlhv-be","yieldMs":5000,"timeout":10}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":151,"output":276,"cacheRead":91575,"cacheWrite":1079,"totalTokens":93081,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776963058088,"responseId":"063980f351881294be44aa2ee3f2a6c9"}}
{"type":"message","id":"63c025df","parentId":"18cba288","timestamp":"2026-04-23T16:51:05.006Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_tkuq2ug4ykzq_1","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"export const COURSE_STATUS = {\n  DRAFT: 'draft',\n  ONGOING: 'ongoing',\n  COMPLETED: 'completed',\n  CANCELED: 'canceled',\n} as const;\n\nexport const COURSE_STATUS_DISPLAY = {\n  [COURSE_STATUS.DRAFT]: 'Sắp khai giảng',\n  [COURSE_STATUS.ONGOING]: 'Đang học',\n  [COURSE_STATUS.COMPLETED]: 'Đã kết thúc',\n  [COURSE_STATUS.CANCELED]: 'Đã hủy',\n} as const;\n\nexport const COURSE_TYPES = {\n  DIRECT: 'trực tiếp',\n  UPGRADE: 'nâng hạng',\n} as const;\n\n/**\n * Mapping of alternative status names to their internal canonical values.\n * Helps maintain consistency during filtering and data ingestion.\n */\nexport const COURSE_STATUS_MAP: Record<string, string> = {\n  'Sắp khai giảng': COURSE_STATUS.DRAFT,\n  'Đang học': COURSE_STATUS.ONGOING,\n  'Đã kết thúc': COURSE_STATUS.COMPLETED,\n  'Sắp KG': COURSE_STATUS.DRAFT,\n  active: COURSE_STATUS.ONGOING,\n  upcoming: COURSE_STATUS.DRAFT,\n  finished: COURSE_STATUS.COMPLETED,\n  ongoing: COURSE_STATUS.ONGOING,\n  draft: COURSE_STATUS.DRAFT,\n  completed: COURSE_STATUS.COMPLETED,\n  canceled: COURSE_STATUS.CANCELED,\n};"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":27,"aggregated":"export const COURSE_STATUS = {\n  DRAFT: 'draft',\n  ONGOING: 'ongoing',\n  COMPLETED: 'completed',\n  CANCELED: 'canceled',\n} as const;\n\nexport const COURSE_STATUS_DISPLAY = {\n  [COURSE_STATUS.DRAFT]: 'Sắp khai giảng',\n  [COURSE_STATUS.ONGOING]: 'Đang học',\n  [COURSE_STATUS.COMPLETED]: 'Đã kết thúc',\n  [COURSE_STATUS.CANCELED]: 'Đã hủy',\n} as const;\n\nexport const COURSE_TYPES = {\n  DIRECT: 'trực tiếp',\n  UPGRADE: 'nâng hạng',\n} as const;\n\n/**\n * Mapping of alternative status names to their internal canonical values.\n * Helps maintain consistency during filtering and data ingestion.\n */\nexport const COURSE_STATUS_MAP: Record<string, string> = {\n  'Sắp khai giảng': COURSE_STATUS.DRAFT,\n  'Đang học': COURSE_STATUS.ONGOING,\n  'Đã kết thúc': COURSE_STATUS.COMPLETED,\n  'Sắp KG': COURSE_STATUS.DRAFT,\n  active: COURSE_STATUS.ONGOING,\n  upcoming: COURSE_STATUS.DRAFT,\n  finished: COURSE_STATUS.COMPLETED,\n  ongoing: COURSE_STATUS.ONGOING,\n  draft: COURSE_STATUS.DRAFT,\n  completed: COURSE_STATUS.COMPLETED,\n  canceled: COURSE_STATUS.CANCELED,\n};","cwd":"/root/.openclaw/workspaces2/projects/ahv-qlhv-be"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1776963064999}}
{"type":"message","id":"9b5de9d9","parentId":"63c025df","timestamp":"2026-04-23T16:51:15.155Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I have a clear picture. Let me implement:\n\n**Backend plan:**\n1. Add method `getTodayMilestones(teacherId)` in `CourseService` - gets courses starting/ending today for a teacher\n2. Add method `bulkUpdateCourseStatus(courseIds, newStatus)` in `CourseService`\n3. Add controller endpoints:\n   - `GET /api/v1/courses/today-milestones` - get today's opening/closing courses\n   - `POST /api/v1/courses/bulk-update-status` - bulk update status\n   - `GET /api/v1/courses/for-review` - get courses for manual review (with pagination)\n   - `PUT /api/v1/courses/:id/status` - update single course status\n\n**Frontend plan:**\n1. Create `CourseMilestoneBanner.tsx` component\n2. Add it to `Dashboard.tsx`\n3. Add handlers for auto-update and manual review\n\nNow let me start implementing. First, I'll set up the backend service and controller methods, then move to the frontend component.\n\nSetting up the repository query to filter courses by teacher's enrollment dates... Finishing the aggregation pipeline to populate course details and enrollment information, then sorting by creation date with pagination support. Now I'm writing the actual implementation code.","thinkingSignature":"3400966d79b5fdff10e41b229d8aed9fed1f65d55f82fc741e3cd981a9880352"},{"type":"text","text":"Mình hiểu rõ cấu trúc rồi. Bắt đầu implement.\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_bd5kotwmc66t_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"grep -n \"getAllCourses\\|async.*course\\|CourseModel\" src/application/services/course.service.ts | head -20","workdir":"/root/.openclaw/workspaces2/projects/ahv-qlhv-be","yieldMs":5000,"timeout":10}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_bd5kotwmc66t_2","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"grep -n \"export const\" src/interface/controllers/course.controller.ts","workdir":"/root/.openclaw/workspaces2/p