{"type":"message","id":"4e0c3ac2","parentId":"f250fcb7","timestamp":"2026-04-23T16:51:37.413Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now let me implement the feature. I'll add:\n\n1. `getTodayMilestones(teacherId)` in `CourseService` - with the aggregation query directly in the service (since it's a specific query)\n2. `bulkUpdateCourseStatus(courseIds, newStatus, teacherId)` in `CourseService`\n3. Controller methods\n4. Routes\n5. Frontend banner component\n\nLet me start writing the backend code. I'll add the service methods.","thinkingSignature":"e038682e57934cb584c399891e63f0dd88b580fe8efe276cab697570e5b7ee4d"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_n3k3lkti3o5c_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"git checkout -b feat/course-milestone-notification-20260423","workdir":"/root/.openclaw/workspaces2/projects/ahv-qlhv-be","yieldMs":10000,"timeout":30}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":193,"output":182,"cacheRead":94615,"cacheWrite":761,"totalTokens":95751,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776963091491,"responseId":"06398114f19b5ef5d926acae0413e4ab"}}
