{"type":"message","id":"79023da2","parentId":"37e11be4","timestamp":"2026-04-23T16:54:02.084Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_3f72w23lorut_1","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"\n      <StudentDetailDrawer\n        isOpen={!!selectedStudent}\n        student={selectedStudent}\n        onClose={() => setSelectedStudent(null)}\n      />\n\n      {/* WELCOME POPUP MODAL */}\n      {showWelcome && (\n        <div className=\"fixed inset-0 z-[100] flex items-center justify-center p-4 bg-gray-900/60 backdrop-blur-md animate-in fade-in duration-500\">\n          <div className=\"bg-white rounded-3xl w-full max-w-md shadow-2xl overflow-hidden relative animate-in zoom-in-95 duration-500 ease-out\">\n            <div className=\"absolute top-0 left-0 w-full h-32 bg-gradient-to-br from-indigo-500 to-purple-600\" />\n\n            <button\n              onClick={() => setShowWelcome(false)}\n              className=\"absolute top-4 right-4 p-2 bg-white/20 hover:bg-white/40 rounded-full text-white backdrop-blur-sm transition-all z-10\"\n            >\n              <X className=\"w-4 h-4\" />\n            </button>\n\n            <div className=\"relative pt-16 px-8 pb-10 flex flex-col items-center text-center\">\n              <div className=\"w-24 h-24 bg-white rounded-full p-1.5 shadow-xl mb-6 flex items-center justify-center border-4 border-white\">\n                <div className=\"w-full h-full bg-gradient-to-br from-indigo-50 to-indigo-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-indigo-600 font-black text-3xl\">\n                  {user?.first_name?.[0]?.toUpperCase() || 'A'}\n                </div>\n              </div>\n\n              <div className=\"inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 px-3 py-1 rounded-full bg-emerald-50 border border-emerald-100 text-emerald-600 text-[10px] font-black uppercase tracking-widest mb-4\">\n                <Sparkles className=\"w-3 h-3\" />\n                Đăng nhập thành công\n              </div>\n\n              <h3 className=\"text-2xl font-black text-gray-900 tracking-tight leading-tight\">\n                Chào mừng quay trở lại,\n                <br />\n                <span className=\"text-indigo-600\">\n                  {user?.last_name} {user?.first_name}!\n                </span>\n              </h3>\n\n              <p className=\"text-gray-500 font-medium text-sm mt-3 px-4\">\n                Hôm nay bạn có một ngày làm việc tuyệt vời nhé. Hệ thống đã chuẩn bị sẵn sàng các báo cáo mới nhất.\n              </p>\n\n              <button\n                onClick={() => setShowWelcome(false)}\n                className=\"w-full mt-8 px-6 py-4 bg-indigo-600 text-white font-black rounded-2xl shadow-xl shadow-indigo-600/20 hover:bg-indigo-700 hover:scale-[1.02] active:scale-[0.98] transition-all uppercase tracking-widest text-xs\"\n              >\n                Bắt đầu công việc\n              </button>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n      )}\n    </motion.div>\n  );\n};\n\nexport default Dashboard;\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1776963242078}}
{"type":"message","id":"685ccfc9","parentId":"79023da2","timestamp":"2026-04-23T16:54:09.963Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I have a good understanding of the dashboard structure. Let me now create the `CourseMilestoneBanner.tsx` component and then add it to the Dashboard.\n\nThe banner should:\n1. Appear when there are courses starting or ending today\n2. Show a non-intrusive card/banner\n3. Have two buttons: \"Tự động\" and \"Cập nhật bằng tay\"\n4. When \"Tự động\" is clicked, show a confirmation, then call the bulk update API\n5. When \"Cập nhật bằng tay\" is clicked, show a modal with the list of courses to review\n\n\n6. I'm building the component with hooks to fetch today's milestones on mount, manage modal visibility, and handle the bulk update flow with a confirmation step.","thinkingSignature":"386201be2bd186635f62a7a19c043d794dfca9a50e699b93b139617e7795e98a"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_bhzus0y0n21g_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"git checkout -b feat/course-milestone-banner-20260423","workdir":"/root/.openclaw/workspaces2/projects/ahv-qlhv-fe","yieldMs":10000,"timeout":30}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":806,"output":263,"cacheRead":100185,"cacheWrite":1214,"totalTokens":102468,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776963242101,"responseId":"063981abde9748b6521411fc56586358"}}
