{"type":"message","id":"df948e26","parentId":"3f3a094f","timestamp":"2026-04-23T17:43:12.103Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"6125\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"6053576134\",\n  \"sender\": \"Khuong\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Thu 2026-04-23 17:42 UTC\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"Khuong (6053576134)\",\n  \"id\": \"6053576134\",\n  \"name\": \"Khuong\",\n  \"username\": \"khuowgn\"\n}\n```\n\nyarn run v1.22.22\n$ ts-node-dev --transpile-only -r tsconfig-paths/register src/index.ts\n[INFO] 17:42:46 ts-node-dev ver. 2.0.0 (using ts-node ver. 10.9.2, typescript ver. 6.0.2)\nError: EMFILE: too many open files, watch '/tmp/.ts-nodeNuDqh9/compiled/5943994464146096.req'\n at FSWatcher.<computed> (node:internal/fs/watchers:254:19)\n at Object.watch (node:fs:2554:36)\n at createFsWatchInstance (/root/.openclaw/workspaces2/projects/ahv-qlhv-be/node_modules/chokidar/lib/nodefs-handler.js:119:15)\n at setFsWatchListener (/root/.openclaw/workspaces2/projects/ahv-qlhv-be/node_modules/chokidar/lib/nodefs-handler.js:166:15)\n at NodeFsHandler._watchWithNodeFs (/root/.openclaw/workspaces2/projects/ahv-qlhv-be/node_modules/chokidar/lib/nodefs-handler.js:331:14)\n at NodeFsHandler._handleFile (/root/.openclaw/workspaces2/projects/ahv-qlhv-be/node_modules/chokidar/lib/nodefs-handler.js:395:23)\n at NodeFsHandler._addToNodeFs (/root/.openclaw/workspaces2/projects/ahv-qlhv-be/node_modules/chokidar/lib/nodefs-handler.js:637:21)\n at async /root/.openclaw/workspaces2/projects/ahv-qlhv-be/node_modules/chokidar/index.js:451:21\n at async Promise.all (index 0) {\n errno: -24,\n syscall: 'watch',\n code: 'EMFILE',\n path: '/tmp/.ts-nodeNuDqh9/compiled/5943994464146096.req',\n filename: '/tmp/.ts-nodeNuDqh9/compiled/5943994464146096.req'\n}\nerror Command failed with exit code 1.\ninfo Visit https://yarnpkg.com/en/docs/cli/run for documentation about this command.\nr