{"type":"message","id":"86dfd057","parentId":"a5c4c59e","timestamp":"2026-04-23T17:53:36.944Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"I see! The `handleSelectStadium` function calls `touch('venueId')` but doesn't re-validate. Looking at the `touch` function:\n```typescript\nconst touch = (k: keyof ExamData) => {\n  setTouched((t) => ({ ...t, [k]: true }));\n  setErrors((e) => ({ ...e, ...validate({ ...form }) }));\n};\n```\n\nThe `touch` function does call `validate` — but it validates the current `form`, not the updated form (with the new stadium selected). This is the bug!\n\nThe fix: after selecting a stadium, call `validate` with the updated form.\n\n\nLet me check if the graduation modal has the same issue.","thinkingSignature":"7ba30f844c8de467ba401302f2d94edec2adffdeec4eb8fb16be2b141767098a"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_p23oanq860j8_1","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/root/.openclaw/workspaces2/projects/ahv-qlhv-fe/src/components/graduation/AddGraduationExamModal.tsx","offset":140,"limit":60}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":557,"output":224,"cacheRead":133492,"cacheWrite":914,"totalTokens":135187,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776966810461,"responseId":"06398f9b984ab11c9994706bb2aab2c0"}}
