{"type":"compaction","id":"a8f2f771","parentId":"cd850d2f","timestamp":"2026-04-23T17:54:31.452Z","summary":"## Goal\n- Fix issues in the AHV QLHV projects (`ahv-qlhv-fe`, `ahv-qlhv-be`) and MAIY Tech Hub ecosystem according to user requests, with branch-per-task and commit-only workflow.\n- Maintain uptime of services: report portal (8790), MAIY Tech Hub frontend (3000), MAIY Tech Hub backend (4000).\n- Current: Implement course milestone notification banner on teacher dashboard (courses starting/ending today).\n\n## Constraints & Preferences\n- Always use prompt-optimizer first to clarify, then confirm with user, then implement.\n- Do not type code directly unless via workflow/agent when possible.\n- Must **checkout a new branch before doing work**.\n- Must **not push**. Only **commit** after finishing.\n- Local only agent ecosystem, no GitLab push.\n- MongoDB only, no PostgreSQL.\n- User language preference: Vietnamese.\n\n## Progress\n### Done\n- [x] **Fixed DAT action disabled on Progress page without enrollment** — `fix/progress-dat-disable-without-enrollment-20260423` → `aedf1f6`\n- [x] **Confirmed health check persistence fix in backend** — `fix/health-profile-update-persist-20260423` → `46afadc`\n- [x] **Fixed add-student course/rank sync** — `fix/student-add-course-rank-sync-20260423` → `963244c`\n- [x] **Fixed \"Đợt thu phí\" settings tab was hidden** — `fix/restore-fee-batch-settings-tab-20260423` → `39f0595`\n- [x] **Synced Student Detail DAT form with Progress page DAT form** — `fix/sync-student-detail-dat-form-with-progress-20260423` → `b499906`\n- [x] **Fixed frontend API base URL for external VPS access** — `fix/external-login-api-base-url-20260423` → `5c6dfe3`\n- [x] **Fixed backend CORS whitelist for external frontend** — `fix/allow-external-fe-cors-20260423` → `48d97e5`\n- [x] **Fixed .env duplicate MongoDB config blocks causing auth failures**\n- [x] **DAT forms — duration/timeStart/timeEnd independent + cross-validation**\n  - Branch: `fix/dat-duration-independent-validation-20260423`\n  - Commit: `782c1bc` — `fix: make duration/timeStart/timeEnd independent in DAT forms, add cross-validation`\n  - Files: `AddDatModal.tsx` (progress page) + `DatSessionModal.tsx` (student detail)\n  - Removed: auto-sync helpers `syncDuration`/`syncEndTime`; default `08:00`/`10:00` on submit\n  - Added: `duration <= (end - start)` validation on submit\n- [x] **Tuition/fee field optional in student profile forms**\n  - `StudentDetailDrawer.tsx` — filtered `tuition` and `fee` from `requiredConfig` in `validateProfile`\n  - `AddStudentModal.tsx` — removed `if (requiredFields.includes('tuition')...)` validation line\n  - Branches: `fix/tuition-fee-optional-20260423` (`848807f`) + `fix/tuition-fee-optional-20260423-2` (`f1d87dc`, `504a89c`)\n- [x] **Health check form — required fields (*) and validation messages**\n  - Branch: `fix/health-check-required-fields-20260423` → `2275548`\n  - File: `src/components/students/StudentDetailDrawer.tsx`\n  - Added: `healthCheckErrors` and `healthCheckTouched` state; `validateHealthCheck()` function\n  - Fields: \"Ngày khám\" and \"Phòng khám / Bệnh viện\" marked `required` with error messages\n  - Logic: validation fires when status != \"Chờ khám\"; clearing errors when status changes to \"Chờ khám\"\n  - Also added `onBlur` prop to `ViDateInput` component (`ViDateInput.tsx`)\n- [x] **Excluded teacher accounts from student list (backend)**\n  - Branch: `fix/exclude-teachers-from-student-list-20260423` → `3aa9d86`\n  - File: `src/infrastructure/repositories/student.repository.ts`\n  - Root cause: `_buildFilters` didn't add `is_deleted: false`; no role-based user filter\n  - Fix: Added `baseFilters.is_deleted = false`; added `$lookup` to `users` collection + `$match` to exclude `_user.role === 'teacher'`\n- [x] **Hided \"Mã HV\" column from student list**\n  - Branch: `fix/hide-student-code-column-20260423` → `6eae2ba`\n  - Files: `StudentTable.tsx` (header) + `StudentTableRow.tsx` (data cell)\n- [x] **Course milestone banner on teacher dashboard (NEW FEATURE)**\n  - BE branch: `feat/course-milestone-notification-20260423` → `49cdcb1`\n  - FE branch: `feat/course-milestone-banner-20260423` → `20ff74e`\n  - Backend: `course.service.ts` — `getTodayMilestones(teacherId)` + `bulkUpdateCourseStatus(courseIds, status, teacherId)`; `course.controller.ts` — `getTodayMilestones` + `bulkUpdateCourseStatus`; `course.routes.ts` — `GET /courses/today-milestones` + `POST /courses/bulk-update-status`\n  - Frontend: new `CourseMilestoneBanner.tsx` component on dashboard; only shown for teacher role; shows opening/closing course counts; two options: \"Tự động cập nhật\" (bulk update status: `draft→ongoing`, `ongoing→completed`) and \"Cập nhật bằng tay\" (review modal with checkbox per course)\n  - `courseService.ts` — added `getTodayMilestones()` + `bulkUpdateCourseStatus()` calls\n\n### In Progress\n- [ ] **Test course milestone banner** — needs teacher account login to verify banner appears\n- [ ] **FE TypeScript**: `ViDateInput.tsx` now supports `onBlur` prop (fixed)\n\n### Blocked\n- MAIY Tech Hub backend (4000) crashes on startup: `FastifyError: Plugin did not start in time: 'mongodb'`. Monitor will restart but will keep failing until root cause is fixed.\n- FE production build blocked by existing repo issue: `Cannot find module '@playwright/test'` in `playwright.config.ts`.\n\n## Key Decisions\n- **Health check data belongs to enrollment**: Root cause was backend enrollment-linked persistence logic.\n- **Student Detail DAT blocked at UI when no enrollment**: Prevent invalid add flow instead of relying on backend failure.\n- **Duration and time fields are independent with submission-time validation**: User explicitly wants no auto-sync between duration and time fields; only validate `duration <= (end - start)` on submit.\n- **Tuition/fee always optional**: Filtered both `'tuition'` and `'fee'` from `requiredConfig` — even if settings marks it as required, it should never be enforced.\n- **Course milestone notification is a dashboard banner, not a popup**: To avoid popup fatigue (there are already welcome popup + feature update popup). Non-blocking card on dashboard.\n- **Teacher auto-update uses `bulkUpdateCourseStatus`**: Bulk updates course status from `draft → ongoing` (opening) and `ongoing → completed` (closing).\n- **Course milestones tracked via `CourseStudent.teacher_id` + `Course.start_date/end_date`**: Teacher's enrollments joined with course dates to find today's milestones.\n- **Course milestone banner only shown for `role === 'teacher'`**: Checks `localStorage` user role before fetching API.\n\n## Next Steps\n1. Test course milestone banner with teacher account login\n2. Consider squashing/ganging related fix branches for cleaner commit history\n3. Fix MAIY Tech Hub backend MongoDB plugin startup timeout (port 4000)\n\n## Critical Context\n- Khuong / Khương Nịnh, prefers Vietnamese.\n- FE: `/root/.openclaw/workspaces2/projects/ahv-qlhv-fe`\n- BE: `/root/.openclaw/workspaces2/projects/ahv-qlhv-be`\n- MAIY FE: `/root/.openclaw/workspaces2/v4-ecosystem-review/maiy-tech-hub` (port 3000)\n- MAIY BE: `/root/.openclaw/workspaces2/projects/maiy-tech-hub-be` (port 4000)\n- Report portal: `/root/.openclaw/workspaces2/v4-ecosystem-review/master-orchestrator/docs/report-portal` (port 8790)\n- Current BE `.env`: `MONGODB_URI=mongodb://103.253.21.98:27017`, `MONGODB_NAME=dtlx`, `JWT_SECRET=super_secret_jwt_key_at_least_32_chars_1234`\n- Services monitor scripts: `/root/.openclaw/workspaces2/v4-ecosystem-review/master-orchestrator/scripts/`\n- Cron for monitor: `* * * * * /root/.openclaw/workspaces2/v4-ecosystem-review/master-orchestrator/scripts/monitor-services.sh`\n- All new AHV QLHV commits are **unpushed** — user has not pushed any of today's changes\n- `ViDateInput` component: `/root/.openclaw/workspaces2/projects/ahv-qlhv-fe/src/components/shared/ViDateInput.tsx` — now has `onBlur` prop added\n- Course `status` values: `'draft'` = \"Sắp khai giảng\", `'ongoing'` = \"Đang học\", `'completed'` = \"Đã kết thúc\"\n- Course `status_detail` (in `CourseStudent`): per-enrollment status like \"Chờ KSK\", \"Đang học\"\n- Teacher accounts excluded from student list via `$match: { '_user.role': { $ne: 'teacher' } }` in aggregate pipeline\n\n---\n\n**Turn Context (split turn):**\n\n## Original Request\nThe user (Khuong) is requesting to see a notification or demo - they say they haven't been able to see a notification and want it to be displayed or demonstrated.\n\n## Early Progress\n- This appears to be the beginning of the conversation (first message)\n- No prior context or AI responses present in this turn\n\n## Context for Suffix\n- The user is asking for visual confirmation of something (likely a notification feature or UI element)\n- They want either the notification to appear or a demo to be shown\n\n<read-files>\n/root/.openclaw/workspaces2/projects/ahv-qlhv-be/src/application/services/dat.service.ts\n/root/.openclaw/workspaces2/projects/ahv-qlhv-be/src/infrastructure/database/models/course_student.model.ts\n/root/.openclaw/workspaces2/projects/ahv-qlhv-be/src/infrastructure/database/models/dat_session.model.ts\n/root/.openclaw/workspaces2/projects/ahv-qlhv-be/src/infrastructure/database/models/student.model.ts\n/root/.openclaw/workspaces2/projects/ahv-qlhv-be/src/infrastructure/database/mongodb.ts\n/root/.openclaw/workspaces2/projects/ahv-qlhv-be/src/infrastructure/utils/queryFilters.ts\n/root/.openclaw/workspaces2/projects/ahv-qlhv-be/src/interface/controllers/auth.controller.ts\n/root/.openclaw/workspaces2/projects/ahv-qlhv-be/src/interface/controllers/dat.controller.ts\n/root/.openclaw/workspaces2/projects/ahv-qlhv-be/src/interface/controllers/student.controller.ts\n/root/.openclaw/workspaces2/projects/ahv-qlhv-be/src/interface/dtos/student.dto.ts\n/root/.openclaw/workspaces2/projects/ahv-qlhv-be/src/interface/routes/dat.routes.ts\n/root/.openclaw/workspaces2/projects/ahv-qlhv-be/sr