al.tsx** (tốt nghiệp): tương tự\n\n## Các branches hiện tại (chưa push)\n- `fix/progress-dat-disable-without-enrollment-20260423` → `aedf1f6`\n- `fix/health-profile-update-persist-20260423` → `46afadc`\n- `fix/student-add-course-rank-sync-20260423` → `963244c`\n- `fix/restore-fee-batch-settings-tab-20260423` → `39f0595`\n- `fix/sync-student-detail-dat-form-with-progress-20260423` → `b499906`\n- `fix/external-login-api-base-url-20260423` → `5c6dfe3`\n- `fix/allow-external-fe-cors-20260423` → `48d97e5`\n- `fix/dat-duration-independent-validation-20260423` → `782c1bc`\n- `fix/tuition-fee-optional-20260423` → `504a89c`\n- `fix/health-check-required-fields-20260423` → `2275548`\n- `fix/exclude-teachers-from-student-list-20260423` → `3aa9d86`\n- `fix/hide-student-code-column-20260423` → `6eae2ba`\n- `feat/course-milestone-notification-20260423` → `49cdcb1`\n- `feat/course-milestone-banner-20260423` → `20ff74e`\n- `fix/course-date-validation-max-students-20260423` → `99ebb02`\n- `fix/course-date-validation-20260423` → `ee2d495`\n\n## Lỗi đã xử lý hôm nay\n- `EMFILE: too many open files` — do MAIY BE có hàng trăm ts-node processes chạy ngầm, chiếm hết file watchers. Đã kill triệt để.\n- Frontend demo banner: tạm bật `demoMode: true` trong `Dashboard.tsx` để user xem — cần gỡ sau khi user approve\n"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":548,"output":1120,"cacheRead":27437,"cacheWrite":234,"totalTokens":29339,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776967401511,"responseId":"063991eb66dd449720c7ddb21b5002dd"}}
