{"type":"message","id":"f307ecd2","parentId":"b84869b6","timestamp":"2026-04-23T18:03:52.391Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user wants to update the course milestone logic to also notify about courses from past days that haven't been updated yet - not just courses with milestones today. So the banner should show all courses that:\n1. Started today OR before today but still in draft status (should have been ongoing but weren't updated)\n2. Ended today OR before today but still in ongoing status (should have been completed but weren't updated)\n\nThis is a more comprehensive \"catch-up\" notification system. I need to:\n1. Update the BE `getTodayMilestones` to also include overdue courses (past start_date not updated, past end_date not updated)\n2. Update the FE banner text to reflect this\n\n\n3. Refine the query logic...\n\nLet me check how the current implementation identifies milestones.","thinkingSignature":"53afe8c8a5bccc0d48b8fb9babbd5a594dd6b328fc0b3f31dc2287990d7d7df0"},{"type":"text","text":"Hiểu rồi. Mình cập nhật logic để bắt cả những khóa **quá hạn cập nhật** (trước hôm nay mà chưa chuyển trạng thái).\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_eta03wm4dqiy_1","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/root/.openclaw/workspaces2/projects/ahv-qlhv-be/src/application/services/course.service.ts","offset":1,"limit":80}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":107,"output":289,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":51754,"totalTokens":52150,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776967423240,"responseId":"06399200fb3ed24451adf2f104e0aa13"}}
{"type":"message","id":"d9eca9c2","parentId":"f307ecd2","timestamp":"2026-04-23T18:03:52.429Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_eta03wm4dqiy_1","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"import { CourseRepository } from '@/infrastructure/repositories/course.repository';\nimport { CourseModel } from '@/infrastructure/database/models/course.model';\nimport { ICourse } from '@/infrastructure/database/models/course.model';\nimport { StudentRepository } from '@/infrastructure/repositories/student.repository';\nimport { ExcelHelper } from '@/infrastructure/utils/excel.helper';\nimport { Response } from 'express';\nimport mongoose from 'mongoose';\nimport { LicenseCategoryModel } from '../../infrastructure/database/models/license_category.model';\nimport { CourseStudentModel } from '../../infrastructure/database/models/course_student.model';\nimport { PaginationOptions } from '@/domain/types/pagination.types';\nimport { COURSE_STATUS_DISPLAY, COURSE_TYPES } from '@/domain/constants/course.constants';\nimport { NotifyService } from './notify.service';\nimport fs from 'fs';\nimport { AppError } from '@/domain/exceptions/app-error';\n\nexport class CourseService {\n  private courseRepository: CourseRepository;\n  private studentRepository: StudentRepository;\n  private excelHelper: ExcelHelper;\n  private notifyService: NotifyService;\n\n  constructor() {\n    this.courseRepository = new CourseRepository();\n    this.studentRepository = new StudentRepository();\n    this.excelHelper = new ExcelHelper();\n    this.notifyService = new NotifyService();\n  }\n\n  async getAllCourses(filters = {}, options: PaginationOptions = { page: 1, limit: 10 }, currentUser?: any) {\n    return await this.courseRepository.findAll(filters, options, currentUser);\n  }\n\n  async getCourseById(id: string, currentUser?: any) {\n    const course = await this.courseRepository.findById(id, currentUser);\n    if (!course) {\n      throw new Error('Không tìm thấy khóa học hoặc bạn không có quyền truy cập');\n    }\n    return course;\n  }\n\n  private async resolveLicenseCategoryId(data: Partial<ICourse>) {\n    if (data.license_category_id && !mongoose.Types.ObjectId.isValid(String(data.license_category_id))) {\n      const val = String(data.license_category_id);\n      let cat = await LicenseCategoryModel.findOne({ code: val });\n      if (!cat) {\n        cat = await LicenseCategoryModel.findOne({ name: val });\n      }\n\n      if (cat) {\n        data.license_category_id = cat._id as any;\n      } else {\n        delete data.license_category_id;\n      }\n    }\n  }\n\n  async createCourse(data: Partial<ICourse>) {\n    if (data.code) {\n      const existingCourse = await this.courseRepository.findByCode(data.code);\n      if (existingCourse) {\n        throw new AppError(`Mã khóa học \"${data.code}\" đã tồn tại trong hệ thống. Vui lòng sử dụng mã khác.`, 400);\n      }\n    }\n    await this.resolveLicenseCategoryId(data);\n    return await this.courseRepository.create(data);\n  }\n\n  async updateCourse(id: string, data: Partial<ICourse>, currentUser?: any) {\n    if (data.code) {\n      const existing = await this.courseRepository.findByCode(data.code);\n      if (existing && existing._id.toString() !== id) {\n        throw new AppError(`Mã khóa học \"${data.code}\" đã tồn tại trong hệ thống. Vui lòng sử dụng mã khác.`, 400);\n      }\n    }\n    await this.resolveLicenseCategoryId(data);\n    return await this.courseRepository.update(id, data);\n  }\n\n  async deleteCourse(id: string, currentUser?: any) {\n    return await this.courseRepository.delete(id);\n\n[263 more lines in file. Use offset=81 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1776967432421}}
