{"type":"message","id":"0db09c0b","parentId":"f4dcd567","timestamp":"2026-04-23T18:04:00.936Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Let me read the `getTodayMilestones` method.","thinkingSignature":"103e12976da8201e407f04e807057389de5d40bd26f8088e033dcec2b374a27e"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_nop0vrq7my0t_1","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/root/.openclaw/workspaces2/projects/ahv-qlhv-be/src/application/services/course.service.ts","offset":240,"limit":80}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":114,"output":80,"cacheRead":51797,"cacheWrite":1223,"totalTokens":53214,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776967436430,"responseId":"0639920e3f5beb55dcffb71ca781de5d"}}
{"type":"message","id":"85d99e95","parentId":"0db09c0b","timestamp":"2026-04-23T18:04:00.955Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_nop0vrq7my0t_1","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"  async getTodayMilestones(teacherId: string) {\n    const teacherOid = new mongoose.Types.ObjectId(teacherId);\n    const today = new Date();\n    today.setHours(0, 0, 0, 0);\n    const tomorrow = new Date(today);\n    tomorrow.setDate(tomorrow.getDate() + 1);\n\n    // Courses starting today (Sắp KG -> Đang học)\n    const openingCourses = await CourseStudentModel.aggregate([\n      { $match: { teacher_id: teacherOid } },\n      {\n        $lookup: {\n          from: 'courseinfos',\n          localField: 'course_id',\n          foreignField: '_id',\n          as: 'course',\n        },\n      },\n      { $unwind: { path: '$course', preserveNullAndEmptyArrays: false } },\n      {\n        $match: {\n          'course.start_date': { $gte: today, $lt: tomorrow },\n          'course.status': 'draft',\n        },\n      },\n      {\n        $project: {\n          _id: '$course._id',\n          name: '$course.name',\n          start_date: '$course.start_date',\n          end_date: '$course.end_date',\n          status: '$course.status',\n          student_count: 1,\n        },\n      },\n    ]);\n\n    // Courses ending today (Đang học -> Đã kết thúc)\n    const closingCourses = await CourseStudentModel.aggregate([\n      { $match: { teacher_id: teacherOid } },\n      {\n        $lookup: {\n          from: 'courseinfos',\n          localField: 'course_id',\n          foreignField: '_id',\n          as: 'course',\n        },\n      },\n      { $unwind: { path: '$course', preserveNullAndEmptyArrays: false } },\n      {\n        $match: {\n          'course.end_date': { $gte: today, $lt: tomorrow },\n          'course.status': 'ongoing',\n        },\n      },\n      {\n        $project: {\n          _id: '$course._id',\n          name: '$course.name',\n          start_date: '$course.start_date',\n          end_date: '$course.end_date',\n          status: '$course.status',\n          student_count: 1,\n        },\n      },\n    ]);\n\n    return {\n      openingCourses,\n      closingCourses,\n      openingCount: openingCourses.length,\n      closingCount: closingCourses.length,\n    };\n  }\n\n  async bulkUpdateCourseStatus(courseIds: string[], newStatus: string, teacherId: string) {\n    const teacherOid = new mongoose.Types.ObjectId(teacherId);\n    const validStatuses = ['draft', 'ongoing', 'completed', 'canceled'];\n    if (!validStatuses.includes(newStatus)) {\n      throw new AppError('Trạng thái không hợp lệ', 400);\n\n[24 more lines in file. Use offset=320 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1776967440948}}
{"type":"message","id":"03ee5f52","parentId":"85d99e95","timestamp":"2026-04-23T18:04:08.769Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I understand the current logic. The user wants to also include overdue courses - courses where:\n1. `start_date < today` AND `status === 'draft'` → should have started already but hasn't been updated to 'ongoing'\n2. `end_date < today` AND `status === 'ongoing'` → should have ended already but hasn't been updated to 'completed'\n\nI need to update the `getTodayMilestones` method to also return these \"overdue\" courses alongside the \"today\" courses.\n\nThe simplest approach:\n- Keep the current logic for \"today\" milestones\n- Add \"overdue\" milestones: courses that passed their start_date or end_date but are still in wrong status\n\n\n- In the response, I'll include both sets of courses and let the frontend display them together, either as separate counts or combined.\n\nNow I'm thinking about how the frontend should handle this - it needs to show both today's milestones and overdue items, then apply the appropriate bulk updates: draft courses with past start dates move to ongoing, and ongoing courses with past end dates move to completed.\n\nUpdating the backend query to fetch both milestone types... Completing the aggregate query to fetch overdue courses by matching on the course status and date criteria, then projecting the necessary fields. Now I need to update the response structure to include both today's milestones and overdue courses, then handle the frontend display logic.","thinkingSignature":"799d688cc8944ea716ffb3689dc8ddbccf41fc332638ade50899449d6b38cc78"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_1uhemaab4oly_1","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/root/.openclaw/workspaces2/projects/ahv-qlhv-fe/src/components/dashboard/CourseMilestoneBanner.tsx","offset":1,"limit":50}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":684,"output":351,"cacheRead":52908,"cacheWrite":247,"totalTokens":54190,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776967440961,"responseId":"0639921219a4ed33b766a68cc2b4e818"}}
{"type":"message","id":"f1a04770","parentId":"03ee5f52","timestamp":"2026-04-23T18:04:08.787Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_1uhemaab4oly_1","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"'use client';\n\nimport React, { useState, useEffect } from 'react';\nimport { CalendarCheck, CalendarX, Zap, Eye, X, CheckCircle2, Loader2 } from 'lucide-react';\nimport { toast } from 'sonner';\nimport { getTodayMilestones, bulkUpdateCourseStatus } from '@/src/services/courseService';\n\ninterface CourseMilestone {\n  _id: string;\n  name: string;\n  start_date?: string;\n  end_date?: string;\n  student_count: number;\n}\n\n// Demo data for testing when no real data available\nconst DEMO_MILESTONES: Milestones = {\n  openingCourses: [\n    { _id: 'demo1', name: 'Khóa B2 - Sáng thứ 2', start_date: new Date().toISOString(), student_count: 28 },\n    { _id: 'demo2', name: 'Khóa B1 - Tối thứ 2', start_date: new Date().toISOString(), student_count: 35 },\n  ],\n  closingCourses: [\n    { _id: 'demo3', name: 'Khóa A1 - Sáng thứ 7', end_date: new Date().toISOString(), student_count: 22 },\n  ],\n  openingCount: 2,\n  closingCount: 1,\n};\n\ninterface Milestones {\n  openingCourses: CourseMilestone[];\n  closingCourses: CourseMilestone[];\n  openingCount: number;\n  closingCount: number;\n}\n\ninterface CourseMilestoneBannerProps {\n  teacherId?: string;\n  /** Force show demo banner (for preview/testing) */\n  demoMode?: boolean;\n}\n\nconst CourseMilestoneBanner: React.FC<CourseMilestoneBannerProps> = ({ demoMode = false }) => {\n  const [milestones, setMilestones] = useState<Milestones | null>(null);\n  const [loading, setLoading] = useState(true);\n  const [processing, setProcessing] = useState(false);\n  const [showReviewModal, setShowReviewModal] = useState(false);\n  const [reviewTab, setReviewTab] = useState<'opening' | 'closing'>('opening');\n  const [selectedCourses, setSelectedCourses] = useState<Set<string>>(new Set());\n  const [dismissed, setDismissed] = useState(false);\n\n\n[265 more lines in file. Use offset=51 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1776967448781}}
{"type":"message","id":"4f52d7ec","parentId":"f1a04770","timestamp":"2026-04-23T18:04:12.604Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Let me also read the rest of the banner to see how it renders the data.","thinkingSignature":"c1f3822d317fdfaf3d1bb9679fae3ada156cd1b4b9ebd0e972f4f731d0b64fd9"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_r1orcpi6h94o_1","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/root/.openclaw/workspaces2/projects/ahv-qlhv-fe/src/components/dashboard/CourseMilestoneBanner.tsx","offset":51,"limit":100}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":585,"output":89,"cacheRead":53070,"cacheWrite":1061,"totalTokens":54805,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776967448793,"responseId":"0639921a199cbaacd503dfd937c83b1b"}}
{"type":"message","id":"e9bacb55","parentId":"4f52d7ec","timestamp":"2026-04-23T18:04:12.622Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_r1orcpi6h94o_1","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"  useEffect(() => {\n    // Demo mode: show demo data immediately\n    if (demoMode) {\n      setMilestones(DEMO_MILESTONES);\n      setLoading(false);\n      return;\n    }\n\n    // Only show for teacher role\n    const stored = localStorage.getItem('user');\n    if (!stored) { setLoading(false); return; }\n    try {\n      const user = JSON.parse(stored);\n      if (user?.role !== 'teacher') { setLoading(false); return; }\n    } catch { setLoading(false); return; }\n\n    getTodayMilestones()\n      .then((res: any) => {\n        if (res?.success && (res.data?.openingCount > 0 || res.data?.closingCount > 0)) {\n          setMilestones(res.data);\n        }\n      })\n      .catch(() => {})\n      .finally(() => setLoading(false));\n  }, [demoMode]);\n\n  if (loading || dismissed) return null;\n  if (!milestones || (milestones.openingCount === 0 && milestones.closingCount === 0)) return null;\n\n  const handleAutoUpdate = async () => {\n    setProcessing(true);\n    try {\n      const promises: Promise<any>[] = [];\n\n      if (milestones.openingCount > 0) {\n        const ids = milestones.openingCourses.map((c) => c._id);\n        promises.push(\n          bulkUpdateCourseStatus(ids, 'ongoing').then((res) => {\n            if (!res?.success) throw new Error(res?.message || 'Lỗi cập nhật khai giảng');\n          })\n        );\n      }\n\n      if (milestones.closingCount > 0) {\n        const ids = milestones.closingCourses.map((c) => c._id);\n        promises.push(\n          bulkUpdateCourseStatus(ids, 'completed').then((res) => {\n            if (!res?.success) throw new Error(res?.message || 'Lỗi cập nhật kết thúc');\n          })\n        );\n      }\n\n      await Promise.all(promises);\n      toast.success('Đã cập nhật trạng thái khóa học tự động!');\n      setDismissed(true);\n      window.dispatchEvent(new CustomEvent('refresh-dashboard'));\n    } catch (err: any) {\n      toast.error(err?.message || 'Có lỗi xảy ra khi cập nhật.');\n    } finally {\n      setProcessing(false);\n    }\n  };\n\n  const handleManualUpdate = () => {\n    setSelectedCourses(new Set());\n    setShowReviewModal(true);\n    setReviewTab(milestones.openingCount > 0 ? 'opening' : 'closing');\n  };\n\n  const handleSubmitManual = async () => {\n    if (selectedCourses.size === 0) {\n      toast.error('Vui lòng chọn ít nhất một khóa học để cập nhật.');\n      return;\n    }\n\n    const newStatus = reviewTab === 'opening' ? 'ongoing' : 'completed';\n    setProcessing(true);\n    try {\n      const res: any = await bulkUpdateCourseStatus(Array.from(selectedCourses), newStatus);\n      if (res?.success) {\n        toast.success('Đã cập nhật trạng thái khóa học!');\n        setShowReviewModal(false);\n        setDismissed(true);\n        window.dispatchEvent(new CustomEvent('refresh-dashboard'));\n      } else {\n        toast.error(res?.message || 'Có lỗi xảy ra.');\n      }\n    } catch (err: any) {\n      toast.error(err?.message || 'Có lỗi xảy ra khi cập nhật.');\n    } finally {\n      setProcessing(false);\n    }\n  };\n\n  const toggleCourse = (id: string) => {\n    setSelectedCourses((prev) => {\n      const next = new Set(prev);\n      if (next.has(id)) next.delete(id);\n      else next.add(id);\n      return next;\n\n[165 more lines in file. Use offset=151 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1776967452615}}
{"type":"message","id":"e14bfbe5","parentId":"e9bacb55","timestamp":"2026-04-23T18:04:29.765Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I understand the full picture. I need to:\n\n1. Update BE `getTodayMilestones` to also return overdue courses (start_date < today but status === 'draft', and end_date < today but status === 'ongoing')\n2. Update FE banner to show overdue courses with a separate badge/section\n\nLet me update the BE first.","thinkingSignature":"d2444a98c6d766359c6b6878bed9ac22f298e2f0a357368fd58201e758548eef"},{"type":"text","text":"Mình cập nhật cả BE và FE để hỗ trợ khóa quá hạn.\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_9apyc6brliwu_1","name":"edit","arguments":{"path":"/root/.openclaw/workspaces2/projects/ahv-qlhv-be/src/application/services/course.service.ts","edits":[{"oldText":"  async getTodayMilestones(teacherId: string) {\n    const teacherOid = new mongoose.Types.ObjectId(teacherId);\n    const today = new Date();\n    today.setHours(0, 0, 0, 0);\n    const tomorrow = new Date(today);\n    tomorrow.setDate(tomorrow.getDate() + 1);\n\n    // Courses starting today (Sắp KG -> Đang học)\n    const openingCourses = await CourseStudentModel.aggregate([\n      { $match: { teacher_id: teacherOid } },\n      {\n        $lookup: {\n          from: 'courseinfos',\n          localField: 'course_id',\n          foreignField: '_id',\n          as: 'course',\n        },\n      },\n      { $unwind: { path: '$course', preserveNullAndEmptyArrays: false } },\n      {\n        $match: {\n          'course.start_date': { $gte: today, $lt: tomorrow },\n          'course.status': 'draft',\n        },\n      },\n      {\n        $project: {\n          _id: '$course._id',\n          name: '$course.name',\n          start_date: '$course.start_date',\n          end_date: '$course.end_date',\n          status: '$course.status',\n          student_count: 1,\n        },\n      },\n    ]);\n\n    // Courses ending today (Đang học -> Đã kết thúc)\n    const closingCourses = await CourseStudentModel.aggregate([\n      { $match: { teacher_id: teacherOid } },\n      {\n        $lookup: {\n          from: 'courseinfos',\n          localField: 'course_id',\n          foreignField: '_id',\n          as: 'course',\n        },\n      },\n      { $unwind: { path: '$course', preserveNullAndEmptyArrays: false } },\n      {\n        $match: {\n          'course.end_date': { $gte: today, $lt: tomorrow },\n          'course.status': 'ongoing',\n        },\n      },\n      {\n        $project: {\n          _id: '$course._id',\n          name: '$course.name',\n          start_date: '$course.start_date',\n          end_date: '$course.end_date',\n          status: '$course.status',\n          student_count: 1,\n        },\n      },\n    ]);\n\n    return {\n      openingCourses,\n      closingCourses,\n      openingCount: openingCourses.length,\n      closingCount: closingCourses.length,\n    };\n  }","newText":"  async getTodayMilestones(teacherId: string) {\n    const teacherOid = new mongoose.Types.ObjectId(teacherId);\n    const today = new Date();\n    today.setHours(0, 0, 0, 0);\n    const tomorrow = new Date(today);\n    tomorrow.setDate(tomorrow.getDate() + 1);\n\n    // Base pipeline to get teacher's courses with student count\n    const basePipeline = (matchStage: any) => [\n      { $match: { teacher_id: teacherOid } },\n      {\n        $lookup: {\n          from: 'courseinfos',\n          localField: 'course_id',\n          foreignField: '_id',\n          as: 'course',\n        },\n      },\n      { $unwind: { path: '$course', preserveNullAndEmptyArrays: false } },\n      { $match: matchStage },\n      {\n        $project: {\n          _id: '$course._id',\n          name: '$course.name',\n          start_date: '$course.start_date',\n          end_date: '$course.end_date',\n          status: '$course.status',\n          student_count: 1,\n        },\n      },\n    ];\n\n    // 1. Courses starting TODAY (Sắp KG -> Đang học)\n    const openingToday = await CourseStudentModel.aggregate(\n      basePipeline({\n        'course.start_date': { $gte: today, $lt: tomorrow },\n        'course.status': 'draft',\n      })\n    );\n\n    // 2. Courses that SHOULD have started (start_date < today) but still draft — overdue\n    const overdueOpening = await CourseStudentModel.aggregate(\n      basePipeline({\n        'course.start_date': { $lt: today },\n        'course.status': 'draft',\n      })\n    );\n\n    // 3. Courses ending TODAY (Đang học -> Đã kết thúc)\n    const closingToday = await CourseStudentModel.aggregate(\n      basePipeline({\n        'course.end_date': { $gte: today, $lt: tomorrow },\n        'course.status': 'ongoing',\n      })\n    );\n\n    // 4. Courses that SHOULD have ended (end_date < today) but still ongoing — overdue\n    const overdueClosing = await CourseStudentModel.aggregate(\n      basePipeline({\n        'course.end_date': { $lt: today },\n        'course.status': 'ongoing',\n      })\n    );\n\n    return {\n      openingCourses: [...openingToday, ...overdueOpening],\n      closingCourses: [...closingToday, ...overdueClosing],\n      openingCount: openingToday.length + overdueOpening.length,\n      closingCount: closingToday.length + overdueClosing.length,\n      overdueOpeningCount: overdueOpening.length,\n      overdueClosingCount: overdueClosing.length,\n    };\n  }"}]}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":958,"output":1443,"cacheRead":53775,"cacheWrite":971,"totalTokens":57147,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776967452627,"responseId":"0639921e19ad9332c2d75e5d28e3d27c"}}
