{"type":"message","id":"2ce9f4f0","parentId":"a89ffcdf","timestamp":"2026-04-23T18:05:55.506Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is saying that when they first try to submit the form without selecting a stadium (sân thi), they get the error message \"Vui lòng chọn địa điểm hoặc sân thi.\" but after selecting a stadium, the message doesn't hide/disappear.\n\nThis is the validation logic in the exam batch forms (both `AddGraduationExamModal.tsx` and `ExamModal.tsx`). The `validate()` function sets errors, and `touched` state determines whether the error is shown. The problem is likely that when a user selects a stadium, the `venueId` field is set but the `touched` state isn't being updated, so the error still shows.\n\n\nI need to trace through the `handleSelectStadium` function to see if it's properly updating the touched state after a stadium is selected.","thinkingSignature":"bbbc1f0833dbc6ec4f3b72caaa4e31fe25ca29ada473ade0bf232eeefc5b610b"},{"type":"text","text":"Mình kiểm tra ngay.\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_72i8nu6tho6g_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"grep -n \"handleSelectStadium\\|setTouched\\|touch('venueId')\\|touch('location')\\|venueId\\|location\" src/components/sat-hach/ExamModal.tsx | head -20","workdir":"/root/.openclaw/workspaces2/projects/ahv-qlhv-fe","yieldMs":5000,"timeout":10}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":0,"output":303,"cacheRead":59668,"cacheWrite":614,"totalTokens":60585,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776967545991,"responseId":"0639927c8f8c7427eabbecbd02c7ba29"}}
{"type":"message","id":"d5895b5c","parentId":"2ce9f4f0","timestamp":"2026-04-23T18:05:55.541Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_72i8nu6tho6g_1","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"19:  venueId: string;\n38:  venueId: '',\n54:  if (!form.venueId) errs.venueId = 'Vui lòng chọn sân / trung tâm sát hạch.';\n100:  const [touched, setTouched] = useState<Partial<Record<keyof ExamData, boolean>>>({});\n142:          // If venueId is present, make sure it's in the list\n143:          if (data.venueId) {\n145:              const res = await getStadiumById(data.venueId);\n159:        setTouched({});\n169:        updated.venueId = '';\n176:  const handleSelectStadium = (stadium: Stadium) => {\n179:      venueId: stadium._id,\n185:    touch('venueId');\n198:    if (isOpen && initial?.venueId) {\n199:      initStadium(initial.venueId);\n206:    setTouched((t) => ({ ...t, [k]: true }));\n212:    setTouched({ name: true, plannedDate: true, venueId: true, region: true });\n229:        stadium_id: form.venueId,\n277:      venueId: 'custom', // Placeholder to pass validation\n283:    touch('venueId');\n367:          <FieldWrapper label=\"Sân / Trung tâm sát hạch\" required field=\"venueId\" touched={touched} errors={errors}>"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":14,"aggregated":"19:  venueId: string;\n38:  venueId: '',\n54:  if (!form.venueId) errs.venueId = 'Vui lòng chọn sân / trung tâm sát hạch.';\n100:  const [touched, setTouched] = useState<Partial<Record<keyof ExamData, boolean>>>({});\n142:          // If venueId is present, make sure it's in the list\n143:          if (data.venueId) {\n145:              const res = await getStadiumById(data.venueId);\n159:        setTouched({});\n169:        updated.venueId = '';\n176:  const handleSelectStadium = (stadium: Stadium) => {\n179:      venueId: stadium._id,\n185:    touch('venueId');\n198:    if (isOpen && initial?.venueId) {\n199:      initStadium(initial.venueId);\n206:    setTouched((t) => ({ ...t, [k]: true }));\n212:    setTouched({ name: true, plannedDate: true, venueId: true, region: true });\n229:        stadium_id: form.venueId,\n277:      venueId: 'custom', // Placeholder to pass validation\n283:    touch('venueId');\n367:          <FieldWrapper label=\"Sân / Trung tâm sát hạch\" required field=\"venueId\" touched={touched} errors={errors}>","cwd":"/root/.openclaw/workspaces2/projects/ahv-qlhv-fe"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1776967555533}}
{"type":"message","id":"40209f1c","parentId":"d5895b5c","timestamp":"2026-04-23T18:06:04.751Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"I see the issue. The `touch` function sets `errors` in the `validate` call:\n```tsx\nconst touch = (k: keyof ExamData) => {\n  setTouched((t) => ({ ...t, [k]: true }));\n  setErrors((e) => ({ ...e, ...validate({ ...form }) }));\n};\n```\n\nBut `form` here is a snapshot from the closure, not the latest form state. When `handleSelectStadium` is called:\n1. `setForm` is called to update `venueId`\n2. `touch('venueId')` is called\n\n\n3. Inside `touch`, `validate({ ...form })` uses the old form (before `venueId` is updated)\n\nThe `touch` function closes over `form` from the outer scope, so when `handleSelectStadium` calls `setForm` and then `touch`, the validation runs with the stale form state before the venueId update is applied. I need to call `validate` with the updated form data instead.\n\nThe fix is to pass the updated form to `touch` so validation runs against the latest state. I can either use the functional form of `setErrors` to access the current form, or pass the updated form directly to the validation function.","thinkingSignature":"09059b626480dc789b0d8d53afd37f8f27719b859c532789181a2947526879b3"},{"type":"text","text":"Found it! Lỗi nằm ở hàm `touch` — nó dùng `form` cũ từ closure (chưa có `venueId` mới) khi validate.\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_n1zj5a5tbmh4_1","name":"edit","arguments":{"path":"/root/.openclaw/workspaces2/projects/ahv-qlhv-fe/src/components/sat-hach/ExamModal.tsx","edits":[{"oldText":"  const touch = (k: keyof ExamData) => {\n    setTouched((t) => ({ ...t, [k]: true }));\n    setErrors((e) => ({ ...e, ...validate({ ...form }) }));\n  };\n","newText":"  const touch = (k: keyof ExamData, updatedForm?: ExamData) => {\n    setTouched((t) => ({ ...t, [k]: true }));\n    setErrors((e) => ({ ...e, ...validate(updatedForm ?? form) }));\n  };\n"}]}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":395,"output":518,"cacheRead":60420,"cacheWrite":106,"totalTokens":61439,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776967555547,"responseId":"063992855372f4be624887f4a54114d1"}}
