{"type":"message","id":"377e90ea","parentId":"d5c6e40a","timestamp":"2026-04-23T18:07:50.689Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user says they don't see the overdue badge in the system, even though the database has courses that should qualify. Let me check a few things:\n\n1. Is the BE `getTodayMilestones` API returning the correct data?\n2. Is the FE banner calling the API and receiving the data?\n3. Is the `demoMode` still enabled in `Dashboard.tsx`?\n\nWait - I remember I removed `demoMode` from `Dashboard.tsx` when the user said \"ok tuyệt đó bạn hãy tắt demo đi\". So now the banner is in real mode, not demo mode.\n\n\nThe real issue is likely that either the BE API isn't returning overdue courses properly, the teacher account doesn't have courses with dates before today in draft or ongoing status, or the banner simply isn't showing because there's no data to display. I should check if the BE service is actually querying for overdue courses and returning them correctly.","thinkingSignature":"d1761b529dba03b4dee59748a0f0e833a17c78c5233c8a3b8d74b8b7b48fc7e9"},{"type":"text","text":"Mình check API xem backend trả về gì.\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_tcemjhm0zcre_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"curl -s http://localhost:5002/api/v1/courses/today-milestones 2>/dev/null | head -200 || echo \"BE might be down\"","yieldMs":8000,"timeout":12}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":0,"output":290,"cacheRead":63480,"cacheWrite":419,"totalTokens":64189,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776967659650,"responseId":"063992ed507ad2ae49027d1bfe27e1f5"}}
