{"type":"message","id":"ddcfeacb","parentId":"59ae2ae2","timestamp":"2026-04-23T18:08:02.887Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The API requires a token. Let me check what the issue is with the data. Let me first check if there are any courses in the database with the relevant dates and statuses. I need to query MongoDB directly.\n\nActually, the user said they see the banner but not the overdue badge. So the banner IS showing (they can see it). The question is why they don't see the overdue badge.\n\nLet me think about what could be happening:\n1. The banner shows up (because there ARE milestones)\n2. But the overdue courses aren't showing up\n\nThe most likely cause: the `getTodayMilestones` query is working correctly for today's milestones, but the overdue query might be failing or returning empty. \n\nIf the API returns zero overdue courses, the banner wouldn't display the badge at all. Let me test with some seed data to see what's actually happening.","thinkingSignature":"0bc02c4d714cebdef55c400eb15d7265ae8f390d90b4f534a329dd56e39cc68f"},{"type":"text","text":"Banner có hiện nhưng không có badge quá hạn. Mình query database xem có khóa nào quá hạn không.\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_kzl17qy9be5j_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"mongosh \"mongodb://103.253.21.98:27017/dtlx\" --quiet --eval '\nvar today = new Date();\ntoday.setHours(0, 0, 0, 0);\nprint(\"Today: \" + today.toISOString());\n\n// Draft courses with start_date < today (overdue opening)\nvar overdueDraft = db.courseinfos.countDocuments({\n  start_date: { $lt: today },\n  status: \"draft\"\n});\nprint(\"Overdue draft (should be ongoing): \" + overdueDraft);\nif (overdueDraft > 0) {\n  db.courseinfos.find({\n    start_date: { $lt: today },\n    status: \"draft\"\n  }, { name: 1, start_date: 1, status: 1 }).limit(3).forEach(printjson);\n}\n\n// Ongoing courses with end_date < today (overdue closing)\nvar overdueOngoing = db.courseinfos.countDocuments({\n  end_date: { $lt: today },\n  status: \"ongoing\"\n});\nprint(\"Overdue ongoing (should be completed): \" + overdueOngoing);\nif (overdueOngoing > 0) {\n  db.courseinfos.find({\n    end_date: { $lt: today },\n    status: \"ongoing\"\n  }, { name: 1, end_date: 1, status: 1 }).limit(3).forEach(printjson);\n}\n\n// Today's\nvar todayOpen = db.courseinfos.countDocuments({\n  start_date: { $gte: today },\n  status: \"draft\"\n});\nprint(\"Opening today: \" + todayOpen);\n\nvar todayClose = db.courseinfos.countDocuments({\n  end_date: { $gte: today },\n  status: \"ongoing\"\n});\nprint(\"Closing today: \" + todayClose);\n'\n","yieldMs":15000,"timeout":20}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":67,"output":634,"cacheRead":64171,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":64872,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776967670740,"responseId":"063992f83a1adfd3495ec1a260b482d9"}}
