{"type":"message","id":"5de5a2a1","parentId":"b4b63645","timestamp":"2026-04-23T18:09:30.510Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Wait, I should check if `getTodayMilestones` also checks if the teacher_id matches. Let me verify the course data is associated with the teacher.\n\nThe issue might also be that the `teacher_id` in `coursestudents` doesn't match the teacher's `_id`. Let me check.","thinkingSignature":"97aa3c3901e60c6b17b638e6aa213c8018f6f80f89272ead9b907ad1f9a44ef4"},{"type":"text","text":"Verify thêm về teacher_id trong coursestudents:\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_wfunrb50d69v_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"mongosh \"mongodb://root:RYLoQJqsDr4EQIJB@103.253.21.98:27017/dtlx?authSource=admin\" --quiet --eval '\n// Check if teacher_id in coursestudents matches user _id\nvar teachers = db.users.find({ role: \"teacher\" }, { _id: 1, name: 1, email: 1, username: 1 }).limit(5).toArray();\nprint(\"Teachers:\");\nteachers.forEach(function(t) { print(\"  \" + t._id + \" | \" + t.username + \" | \" + t.name); });\n\n// Check coursestudents teacher_ids\nvar csTeacherIds = db.coursestudents.distinct(\"teacher_id\");\nprint(\"\\nDistinct teacher_ids in coursestudents: \" + csTeacherIds.length);\ncsTeacherIds.slice(0, 3).forEach(function(id) { print(\"  \" + id); });\n\n// Check if any courses have teachers in coursestudents\nvar sample = db.coursestudents.find({}).limit(3).toArray();\nprint(\"\\nSample coursestudents:\");\nsample.forEach(function(cs) { printjson(cs); });\n'\n","yieldMs":15000,"timeout":20}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":124,"output":370,"cacheRead":67745,"cacheWrite":1155,"totalTokens":69394,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776967762490,"responseId":"06399353287bebc9fc88012f1bfb1679"}}
