{"type":"message","id":"a757e345","parentId":"1b262d0c","timestamp":"2026-04-23T18:25:47.268Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Still none! The issue is that the `start_date` for course A11 is `2026-04-23`, which is today, not before today. Let me check:\n\n```\nstart_date: 2026-04-23\ntoday: 2026-04-23T00:00:00.000Z\n```\n\n`2026-04-23` in MongoDB (when stored as date) would be `2026-04-23T00:00:00.000Z` (midnight UTC). But the query `{ $lt: today }` where `today = new Date()` which is the current time (18:24 UTC on April 23). So `today` is `2026-04-23T18:24:00.000Z`. The course start_date is `2026-04-23T00:00:00.000Z`. Since `2026-04-23T00:00:00.000Z` < `2026-04-23T18:24:00.000Z`, it SHOULD match the overdue query.\n\n\nBut the result is empty, so let me trace through the actual pipeline with the specific course A11 to see what's happening. The course has start_date 2026-04-23 and status draft, and today is 2026-04-23 at 18:24, so the date comparison should work. I need to verify if the course is actually in the dataset and check what `start_date` looks like in the raw document.\n\nThe real problem might be that A11's start_date is stored as an ISODate at midnight UTC (2026-04-23T00:00:00.000Z), but the query uses `today = new Date()` which includes the current time. Since `ISODate(\"2026-04-23T00:00:00.000Z\")` is less than `ISODate(\"2026-04-23T18:24:00.000Z\")`, the `$lt: today` comparison should catch it, but the course might not be in the query results at all. Let me verify the pipeline is actually including A11 in its results.","thinkingSignature":"a7a606992501dbc3651455338509e8f27c1ce600aa8859026b9488f7957700a8"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_0b66p554uumx_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"mongosh \"mongodb://root:RYLoQJqsDr4EQIJB@103.253.21.98:27017/dtlx?authSource=admin\" --quiet --eval '\nvar teacherOid = ObjectId(\"69e8333ddbb6750f8166f05e\");\nvar today = new Date();\ntoday.setHours(0, 0, 0, 0);\n\nprint(\"Today: \" + today.toISOString());\n\n// Check A11 specifically in pipeline\nvar a11 = db.courses.findOne({ code: \"A11\" });\nprint(\"A11 start_date: \" + a11.start_date);\nprint(\"A11 start_date ISO: \" + new Date(a11.start_date).toISOString());\nprint(\"A11 start_date < today: \" + (new Date(a11.start_date) < today));\n\n// Check if A11 shows in aggregate with current query\nvar withNull = db.coursestudents.aggregate([\n  { $match: { $or: [{ teacher_id: teacherOid }, { teacher_id: null }] } },\n  { $lookup: { from: \"courses\", localField: \"course_id\", foreignField: \"_id\", as: \"course\" } },\n  { $unwind: \"$course\" },\n  { $match: { \"course.status\": \"draft\" } },\n  { $project: { name: \"$course.name\", code: \"$course.code\", start_date: \"$course.start_date\", teacher_id: 1 } },\n  { $limit: 10 }\n]).toArray();\nprint(\"\\nDraft courses with null or teacher teacher_id:\");\nwithNull.forEach(function(c) {\n  var sd = c.start_date ? new Date(c.start_date).toISOString().split(\"T\")[0] : \"null\";\n  print(\"  \" + c.code + \" | \" + c.name + \" | start: \" + sd + \" | tid: \" + c.teacher_id);\n});\n\n// Check: what about draft courses with start_date <= today\nvar overdueDraft = db.coursestudents.aggregate([\n  { $match: { $or: [{ teacher_id: teacherOid }, { teacher_id: null }] } },\n  { $lookup: { from: \"courses\", localField: \"course_id\", foreignField: \"_id\", as: \"course\" } },\n  { $unwind: \"$course\" },\n  { $match: { \"course.status\": \"draft\", \"course.start_date\": { $lte: today } } },\n  { $project: { name: \"$course.name\", code: \"$course.code\", start_date: \"$course.start_date\" } },\n  { $limit: 10 }\n]).toArray();\nprint(\"\\nDraft with start_date <= today:\");\noverdueDraft.forEach(function(c) {\n  var sd = c.start_date ? new Date(c.start_date).toISOString().split(\"T\")[0] : \"null\";\n  print(\"  \" + c.code + \" | \" + c.name + \" | start: \" + sd);\n});\n'\n","yieldMs":15000,"timeout":20}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":89,"output":1148,"cacheRead":127946,"cacheWrite":1174,"totalTokens":130357,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776968730852,"responseId":"0639971ca84bbf48cee1628deb53bb9c"}}
{"type":"message","id":"6f5320db","parentId":"a757e345","timestamp":"2026-04-23T18:25:48.832Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_0b66p554uumx_1","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Today: 2026-04-23T00:00:00.000Z\nA11 start_date: Thu Apr 23 2026 00:00:00 GMT+0000 (Coordinated Universal Time)\nA11 start_date ISO: 2026-04-23T00:00:00.000Z\nA11 start_date < today: false\n\nDraft courses with null or teacher teacher_id:\n  CK12 | C Khóa 12 - Buổi tối | start: 2026-06-14 | tid: null\n  CK12 | C Khóa 12 - Buổi tối | start: 2026-06-14 | tid: null\n  A11 | khóa test22/4 | start: 2026-04-23 | tid: null\n  A11 | khóa test22/4 | start: 2026-04-23 | tid: null\n\nDraft with start_date <= today:\n  A11 | khóa test22/4 | start: 2026-04-23\n  A11 | khóa test22/4 | start: 2026-04-23"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":1542,"aggregated":"Today: 2026-04-23T00:00:00.000Z\nA11 start_date: Thu Apr 23 2026 00:00:00 GMT+0000 (Coordinated Universal Time)\nA11 start_date ISO: 2026-04-23T00:00:00.000Z\nA11 start_date < today: false\n\nDraft courses with null or teacher teacher_id:\n  CK12 | C Khóa 12 - Buổi tối | start: 2026-06-14 | tid: null\n  CK12 | C Khóa 12 - Buổi tối | start: 2026-06-14 | tid: null\n  A11 | khóa test22/4 | start: 2026-04-23 | tid: null\n  A11 | khóa test22/4 | start: 2026-04-23 | tid: null\n\nDraft with start_date <= today:\n  A11 | khóa test22/4 | start: 2026-04-23\n  A11 | khóa test22/4 | start: 2026-04-23","cwd":"/root/.openclaw/workspaces2/v4-ecosystem-review/master-orchestrator"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1776968748824}}
{"type":"message","id":"0209941b","parentId":"6f5320db","timestamp":"2026-04-23T18:26:04.928Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Found the issue! The `today` in the MongoDB query is `2026-04-23T00:00:00.000Z`. The A11 course has `start_date: 2026-04-23T00:00:00.000Z` (same day, midnight). The comparison `A11 start_date < today` is `false` because they're equal.So the overdue query uses `{ $lt: today }` which means `start_date < 2026-04-23T00:00:00.000Z`. But A11's start_date is exactly `2026-04-23T00:00:00.000Z`, so it's NOT less than today.The fix is to use `{ $lte: today }` instead of `{ $lt: today }` for the overdue queries. This will include courses with start_date exactly today.Also, there's another issue: when we query `start_date >= today, $lt: tomorrow` for \"opening today\", A11 with start_date exactly at midnight today won't match because it's not strictly less than tomorrow.Wait, let me think about this more carefully:- `today = 2026-04-23T00:00:00.000Z`\n\n\n- `tomorrow = 2026-04-24T00:00:00.000Z`\n- A11 `start_date = 2026-04-23T00:00:00.000Z`\n\nFor \"opening today\":\n`start_date >= today AND start_date < tomorrow`\n= `2026-04-23T00:00:00 >= 2026-04-23T00:00:00` AND `2026-04-23T00:00:00 < 2026-04-24T00:00:00`\n= `true AND true`\n= `true`\n\nSo A11 SHOULD match the \"opening today\" query! The overdue query uses `{ $lt: today }`, which is `{ $lt: 2026-04-23T00:00:00.000Z }`, and A11's start_date equals today, not less than it. I need to change the overdue query from `{ $lt: today }` to `{ $lte: today }` to catch courses that started today or earlier.\n\nThe user wants courses with start_date today to show as overdue opening courses, not as today's openings. So the fix is using `$lte: today` instead of `$lt: today` in the overdue query.\n\nFor ongoing courses, the same issue applies—the end_date today courses should be in the \"overdue\" category, not in \"closing today\". I need to update both the opening and closing overdue queries to use `$lte: today` instead of `$lt: today`.","thinkingSignature":"00bcafbd2925190dcddef3d9189eb40115648a75836a6f7228edda29b7b7a542"},{"type":"text","text":"Tìm ra lỗi rồi! A11 có `start_date = 2026-04-23` (midnight UTC). Query dùng `$lt: today` (hôm nay 00:00) nên A11 bị loại vì bằng, không nhỏ hơn. Sửa: `start_date <= today` cho overdue:\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_rioqfg71lldw_1","name":"edit","arguments":{"path":"/root/.openclaw/workspaces2/projects/ahv-qlhv-be/src/application/services/course.service.ts","edits":[{"oldText":"    // 2. Courses that SHOULD have started (start_date < today) but still draft — overdue\n    const overdueOpening = await CourseStudentModel.aggregate(\n      basePipeline({\n        'course.start_date': { $lt: today },\n        'course.status': 'draft',\n      })\n    );\n","newText":"    // 2. Courses that SHOULD have started (start_date <= today) but still draft — overdue\n    const overdueOpening = await CourseStudentModel.aggregate(\n      basePipeline({\n        'course.start_date': { $lte: today },\n        'course.status': 'draft',\n      })\n    );\n"},{"oldText":"    // 4. Courses that SHOULD have ended (end_date < today) but still ongoing — overdue\n    const overdueClosing = await CourseStudentModel.aggregate(\n      basePipeline({\n        'course.end_date': { $lt: today },\n        'course.status': 'ongoing',\n      })\n    );\n","newText":"    // 4. Courses that SHOULD have ended (end_date <= today) but still ongoing — overdue\n    const overdueClosing = await CourseStudentModel.aggregate(\n      basePipeline({\n        'course.end_date': { $lte: today },\n        'course.status': 'ongoing',\n      })\n    );\n"}]}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":331,"output":1034,"cacheRead":128488,"cacheWrite":1810,"totalTokens":131663,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776