{"type":"message","id":"ed025451","parentId":"20459420","timestamp":"2026-04-23T18:27:18.379Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The API now returns:- `openingCount: 4` (4 enrollment records, 1 unique course)- `overdueOpeningCount: 2` (2 unique courses in overdue)But wait, `overdueOpeningCount: 2` but we only have 1 unique course (A11 = khóa test22/4). The `overdueOpeningCount` is the total count of enrollment records, not unique courses. Let me think...\n\nActually, looking at the MongoDB query, the `overdueOpening` array has 2 records (because A11 has 2 enrollments, both with `teacher_id: null`). \n\nAh, I see the distinction now—the API is counting enrollment records for the `Count` fields but deduplicating by course `_id` for the actual course arrays. So `openingCount: 4` represents 4 enrollment records matching the opening criteria, while `unique opening courses` filters those down to just 1 distinct course. Similarly, `overdueOpeningCount: 2` tracks 2 enrollment records, but they're both for the same course A11.\n\nActually, I think I've got it—the frontend deduplicates by course `_id` when rendering, so the user sees \"1 khóa khai giảng\" with a badge showing \"2 quá hạn\" from the `overdueOpeningCount` value. That would make sense from a UX perspective.\n\nThough there's a potential issue: if the same course appears in both the \"opening today\" and \"overdue opening\" categories, it could show up twice in the modal, which isn't ideal.\n\nLet me update the backend logic to only include a course in \"overdue\" if it's not already in \"opening today\", or better yet, count unique courses for each category. Actually, looking back at the user's request, they want to see courses with past start dates that haven't been updated to \"ongoing\" status. A course starting today should probably just be in the \"opening today\" category, not marked as overdue—unless the user specifically wants that distinction.\n\nThe `$lte` change fixes the core issue of A11 not showing up, but I should prevent duplicates by excluding courses that are already in \"opening today\" from appearing in \"overdue opening\".","thinkingSignature":"4ddf3034089c41be122d8f99ed9c3088ff81a6165dc762c68e3c832eacb2d861"},{"type":"text","text":"API hoạt động rồi — khóa A11 xuất hiện! Nhưng có duplicate: A11 hiện trong cả \"khai giảng\" (vì start_date = today) và \"quá hạn\" (vì dùng `$lte`). Mình sửa để tránh trùng:\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_y83rvn9gpif0_1","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/root/.openclaw/workspaces2/projects/ahv-qlhv-be/src/application/services/course.service.ts","offset":285,"limit":15}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":137,"output":620,"cacheRead":132848,"cacheWrite":867,"totalTokens":134472,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776968824099,"responseId":"06399779777c7f0ab33ce16e14e74685"}}
