{"type":"message","id":"5b0d8d90","parentId":"4cf050e3","timestamp":"2026-04-23T18:28:34.170Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now the API returns:- `openingCount: 1` (A11 - khóa test22/4, start_date = 2026-04-23)- `overdueOpeningCount: 2` (but these are the 2 enrollment records for A11 with null teacher_id, so the FE will deduplicate to 0 unique overdue courses after the opening courses)Wait, the deduplication happens in the API now (backend), so:- `openingCourses` = deduplicated list = [A11]- `overdueOpeningCount: 2` = count of all overdue enrollment records (not deduplicated)\n\nIn the frontend, `openingCount: 1` and `overdueOpeningCount: 2`. The badge shows `overdueOpeningCount > 0` which is true (2 > 0), so the badge will show \"2 quá hạn\". But A11 is in the \"opening today\" list, not the \"overdue\" list. \n\nSo the badge count won't match what's actually displayed. The real issue is that `overdueOpeningCount` represents 2 enrollment records for the same course (both with null teacher_id), not 2 unique overdue courses. I need to deduplicate the overdue count to match the actual unique courses that are overdue.\n\nUpdating the return object to count unique overdue courses...","thinkingSignature":"a3a58b8b087e26307a1f40141c6304afbd8d502b1d7cfa5d085c79216fc64aa6"},{"type":"text","text":"`overdueOpeningCount: 2` là 2 enrollment records (cùng 1 khóa A11 với 2 bản ghi null teacher_id). Sửa count cho đúng:\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_d68y4wusd2c5_1","name":"edit","arguments":{"path":"/root/.openclaw/workspaces2/projects/ahv-qlhv-be/src/application/services/course.service.ts","edits":[{"oldText":"    return {\n      openingCourses,\n      closingCourses,\n      openingCount: openingCourses.length,\n      closingCount: closingCourses.length,\n      overdueOpeningCount: overdueOpening.length,\n      overdueClosingCount: overdueClosing.length,\n    };\n  }","newText":"    return {\n      openingCourses,\n      closingCourses,\n      openingCount: openingCourses.length,\n      closingCount: closingCourses.length,\n      overdueOpeningCount: overdueOpening.length,\n      overdueClosingCount: overdueClosing.length,\n      overdueOpeningCourses: overdueOpening,\n      overdueClosingCourses: overdueClosing,\n    };\n  }"}]}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":124,"output":525,"cacheRead":136129,"cacheWrite":599,"totalTokens":137377,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776968903953,"responseId":"063997c9009bbfbe5bfce2d9e286cf57"}}
