{"type":"message","id":"8eca6e73","parentId":"29dd3278","timestamp":"2026-04-23T18:28:45.490Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I also need to update the FE to show overdue courses separately from the main list. But actually, the user said the overdue courses should be included in the milestone notification. So the FE should show ALL milestone courses (both today + overdue) in the combined list.\n\nLet me re-think the UX:\n1. The combined list shows all courses that need to be updated\n2. The \"overdue\" badge shows how many are overdue (start_date < today)\n3. The user can filter between \"khai giảng\" and \"kết thúc\" tabs\n\nFor the \"khai giảng\" tab, it should show BOTH courses starting today AND courses that should have started but haven't been updated. These are all \"khai giảng\" courses.\n\n\nThe combined list should merge the today and overdue courses, with the badge displaying the overdue count separately. The FE needs to pass the overdue data to the component so it can display them together with the appropriate badge count. to display the overdue courses in the modal and show the badge with the overdue count. The simplest fix is to deduplicate the overdueOpeningCount in the backend before returning it, so the badge displays accurately without breaking the API contract.","thinkingSignature":"0602e7d1ad2c411c3fefd46cfd3e4d29f7e72d6601eb242e253dd0ee7eac237c"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_hbvo7kwx8o73_1","name":"edit","arguments":{"path":"/root/.openclaw/workspaces2/projects/ahv-qlhv-be/src/application/services/course.service.ts","edits":[{"oldText":"    return {\n      openingCourses,\n      closingCourses,\n      openingCount: openingCourses.length,\n      closingCount: closingCourses.length,\n      overdueOpeningCount: overdueOpening.length,\n      overdueClosingCount: overdueClosing.length,\n      overdueOpeningCourses: overdueOpening,\n      overdueClosingCourses: overdueClosing,\n    };\n  }","newText":"    return {\n      openingCourses,\n      closingCourses,\n      openingCount: openingCourses.length,\n      closingCount: closingCourses.length,\n      overdueOpeningCount: new Set(overdueOpening.map((c: any) => (c._id as any).toString())).size,\n      overdueClosingCount: new Set(overdueClosing.map((c: any) => (c._id as any).toString())).size,\n    };\n  }"}]}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":106,"output":495,"cacheRead":136396,"cacheWrite":922,"totalTokens":137919,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776968914277,"responseId":"063997d43e4256b8a40772b52ea81698"}}
