{"type":"message","id":"a6b7ead4","parentId":"58475afd","timestamp":"2026-04-23T18:32:11.298Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Let me read the `bulkUpdateCourseStatus` method more carefully.","thinkingSignature":"30e1a7215378db83a4067903a24dff889bb04801a7998aaed5a37a0383394168"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_sypvg0miz3kd_1","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/root/.openclaw/workspaces2/projects/ahv-qlhv-be/src/application/services/course.service.ts","offset":332,"limit":30}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":0,"output":82,"cacheRead":135650,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":135732,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776969126234,"responseId":"063998a8730fe6ba4a40f50ea397778c"}}
{"type":"message","id":"203cf0f8","parentId":"a6b7ead4","timestamp":"2026-04-23T18:32:11.314Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_sypvg0miz3kd_1","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"  async bulkUpdateCourseStatus(courseIds: string[], newStatus: string, teacherId: string) {\n    const teacherOid = new mongoose.Types.ObjectId(teacherId);\n    const validStatuses = ['draft', 'ongoing', 'completed', 'canceled'];\n    if (!validStatuses.includes(newStatus)) {\n      throw new AppError('Trạng thái không hợp lệ', 400);\n    }\n\n    // Verify teacher owns these courses before updating\n    const courseOids = courseIds.map((id) => new mongoose.Types.ObjectId(id));\n    const enrolledCourses = await CourseStudentModel.distinct('course_id', {\n      teacher_id: teacherOid,\n      course_id: { $in: courseOids },\n    });\n\n    const validCourseIds = enrolledCourses.map((id) => id.toString());\n    const unauthorized = courseIds.filter((id) => !validCourseIds.includes(id));\n    if (unauthorized.length > 0) {\n      throw new AppError('Bạn không có quyền cập nhật một số khóa học', 403);\n    }\n\n    const result = await CourseModel.updateMany(\n      { _id: { $in: courseOids } },\n      { $set: { status: newStatus, updated_at: new Date() } }\n    );\n\n    return { updated: result.modifiedCount, courseIds: validCourseIds };\n  }\n}\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1776969131308}}
{"type":"message","id":"f426ec8f","parentId":"203cf0f8","timestamp":"2026-04-23T18:32:19.417Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Found the issue! The `bulkUpdateCourseStatus` method verifies that the teacher owns the courses by checking `teacher_id` in `coursestudents`. But A11's enrollment records have `teacher_id: null` — not the teacher's ObjectId.\n\nSo the check `teacher_id: teacherOid` fails for A11 because its enrollment has `teacher_id: null`.\n\nI need to fix the authorization check to also allow courses with `teacher_id: null` (unassigned courses).","thinkingSignature":"1e6398a17d90361a08413ca8af69e38974681db17b55115336b6fb94218e6d5e"},{"type":"text","text":"\nTìm ra lỗi rồi! `bulkUpdateCourseStatus` check `teacher_id: teacherOid` trong `coursestudents`, nhưng A11 có `teacher_id: null` → bị từ chối quyền.\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_ua8zs70bwozo_1","name":"edit","arguments":{"path":"/root/.openclaw/workspaces2/projects/ahv-qlhv-be/src/application/services/course.service.ts","edits":[{"oldText":"    // Verify teacher owns these courses before updating\n    const courseOids = courseIds.map((id) => new mongoose.Types.ObjectId(id));\n    const enrolledCourses = await CourseStudentModel.distinct('course_id', {\n      teacher_id: teacherOid,\n      course_id: { $in: courseOids },\n    });\n","newText":"    // Verify teacher owns these courses before updating\n    // Allow both courses assigned to this teacher AND unassigned courses (teacher_id: null)\n    const courseOids = courseIds.map((id) => new mongoose.Types.ObjectId(id));\n    const enrolledCourses = await CourseStudentModel.distinct('course_id', {\n      $or: [{ teacher_id: teacherOid }, { teacher_id: null }],\n      course_id: { $in: courseOids },\n    });\n"}]}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":377,"output":408,"cacheRead":135266,"cacheWrite":407,"totalTokens":136458,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776969131327,"responseId":"063998ad4f0947d372e3314261c649a4"}}
