{"type":"message","id":"789b48fe","parentId":"c8eb54c1","timestamp":"2026-04-23T18:38:48.735Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Both have lint and build scripts. Let me now set up the workflow. I'll create a helper function for GitLab MR creation and merge waiting.\n\nLet me start the sequential workflow:\n\n**BE Branches in order:**\n1. `fix/course-date-validation-max-students-20260423`\n2. `fix/exam-batch-required-validation-20260423`  \n3. `feat/course-milestone-notification-20260423`\n4. `fix/exclude-teachers-from-student-list-20260423`\n5. `fix/allow-external-fe-cors-20260423`\n\n\n6. `fix/health-profile-update-persist-20260423`\n\n**FE Branches in order:**\n1. `fix/course-date-validation-20260423`\n2. `feat/course-milestone-banner-20260423`\n3. `fix/health-check-required-fields-20260423`\n4. `fix/tuition-fee-optional-20260423-2`\n5. `fix/hide-student-code-column-20260423`\n6. `fix/dat-duration-independent-validation-20260423`\n\nNow I need to consolidate the branches that address similar issues.\n\nLooking at the BE branches, I see some overlap—`fix/course-date-validation-max-students-20260423` and `fix/exam-batch-required-validation-20260423` both contain overdue detection and milestone notification fixes, so I should merge those first. Then I'll handle the remaining BE branches separately: the external CORS fix, health profile persistence, and the exam batch required validation branch that also addresses venue and milestone issues.\n\nFor the FE side, I'm consolidating `fix/course-date-validation-20260423` with the course milestone banner branch since they both have the AuthContext fix and milestone updates, then proceeding with the health check, tuition, and student code fixes.\n\nNow I'm mapping out the complete push order for both backends and frontends, starting with the BE date validation branch and working through all the fixes systematically.","thinkingSignature":"91a788a076417117e922c028c40d8396923cdad7b1a8c20e6930b2c421e244cd"},{"type":"text","text":"Tất cả đều có lint + build. Bắt đầu BE — branch đầu tiên:\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_nak9bg6a1u4i_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"TOKEN=\"glpat-c_N4qQVxbcktRro-S5rdwGM6MQpvOjEKdTpoZDBsYg8.01.170axqn65\"\nBE_PROJECT_ID=\"81078323\"\n\n# === BRANCH 1: fix/course-date-validation-max-students-20260423 ===\necho \"===== BE: fix/course-date-validation-max-students-20260423 =====\"\ncd /root/.openclaw/workspaces2/projects/ahv-qlhv-be\ngit checkout develop && git pull origin develop\ngit checkout fix/course-date-validation-max-students-20260423\n\n# Merge develop\ngit merge develop --no-edit 2>&1 | tail -5\necho \"Merge done\"","yieldMs":30000,"timeout":60}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":148,"output":635,"cacheRead":140744,"cacheWrite":764,"totalTokens":142291,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776969514665,"responseId":"06399a2c392c75ff2c4b5f293aa4e36a"}}
